										<content:encoded><![CDATA[
<h1 class="has-text-align-center"><strong>Marketing de Harry’s: Lo que aprendimos al aplicar ingeniería inversa a una startup de $400 millones (estudio de caso)</strong></h1>
<div class="post-content-category"><a href="https://sleeknote.com/es/blog/category/growth-marketing" rel="category tag">Growth Marketing</a></div>


<figure class="wp-block-image alignwide size-large"><img width="1024" height="437" src="http://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/Harrys-Marketing-WordPress-2-1024x437.jpg" alt="Harry’s Marketing [WordPress]" class="wp-image-115043" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/Harrys-Marketing-WordPress-2-1024x437.jpg 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/Harrys-Marketing-WordPress-2-300x128.jpg 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/Harrys-Marketing-WordPress-2-768x328.jpg 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/Harrys-Marketing-WordPress-2-1536x656.jpg 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/Harrys-Marketing-WordPress-2-380x162.jpg 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/Harrys-Marketing-WordPress-2-600x256.jpg 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/Harrys-Marketing-WordPress-2-760x325.jpg 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/Harrys-Marketing-WordPress-2-1440x615.jpg 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/Harrys-Marketing-WordPress-2-960x410.jpg 960w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/Harrys-Marketing-WordPress-2-82x35.jpg 82w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/Harrys-Marketing-WordPress-2-117x50.jpg 117w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/Harrys-Marketing-WordPress-2-740x316.jpg 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/Harrys-Marketing-WordPress-2-220x94.jpg 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/Harrys-Marketing-WordPress-2-385x164.jpg 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/Harrys-Marketing-WordPress-2.jpg 1920w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure>


<div id="preamble-block_5fd086618bec4" class="block-preamble"><p>¿Has escuchado sobre <a href="https://www.harrys.com/en/us" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">Harry’s</a>? Desde la fundación de la compañía en 2013, los cofundadores Jeff Raider y Andy Katz-Mayfield han convertido su servicio de suscripción de afeitado en una potencia online global.</p>
</div>






<p>Y los números no mienten:</p>



<ul><li>$250 millones en capital de riesgo (<a href="https://www.inc.com/magazine/201605/bernhard-warner/harrys-razors-german-factory.html" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">I</a><a href="https://www.inc.com/magazine/201605/bernhard-warner/harrys-razors-german-factory.html" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener nofollow">nc.</a>)</li><li>$200 millones en ingresos solo en 2017 (<a href="http://www.adweek.com/creativity/harrys-shaving-brand-tells-its-whole-unlikely-story-fun-long-form-ad-175335/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener nofollow">Adweek</a>)</li><li>3 millones de clientes recurrentes mensuales y contando (<a href="https://www.linkedin.com/company/harry%27s-grooming/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener nofollow">LinkedIn</a>)</li></ul>



<p>Pero lo más interesante, y en lo que quiero que enfoques tu atención, es su estrategia de marketing. No porque sea algo nuevo. Sino, más bien, porque es aplicable a cualquier tienda de e-commerce, independientemente de su tamaño.</p>



<p>Recientemente pasé un mes aplicando ingeniería inversa a la estrategia de marketing de Harry&#8217;s, y hoy <strong>quiero mostrarte cinco estrategias comprobadas que puedes usar para obtener más engagement y conversiones más altas.</strong>&nbsp;</p>



<p>¿La mejor parte? Funcionan incluso si no tienes capital de riesgo o un presupuesto multimillonario para marketing.</p>



<p>¿Suena bien?</p>



<p>Comencemos.</p>


<div id="contentupgrade-block_5fcf568a3dfe7" class="block-content-upgrade">
