<p>Los videos de unboxing de Casper son tan populares que tienen millones de visualizaciones solo en YouTube, lo que resulta en publicidad gratuita para la compañía.</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="488" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/6-Casper-Unboxing-Video-1024x488.png" alt="6 Casper Unboxing Video" class="wp-image-113761" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/6-Casper-Unboxing-Video-1024x488.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/6-Casper-Unboxing-Video-300x143.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/6-Casper-Unboxing-Video-768x366.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/6-Casper-Unboxing-Video-1536x732.png 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/6-Casper-Unboxing-Video-2048x976.png 2048w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/6-Casper-Unboxing-Video-380x181.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/6-Casper-Unboxing-Video-600x286.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/6-Casper-Unboxing-Video-760x362.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/6-Casper-Unboxing-Video-1440x686.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/6-Casper-Unboxing-Video-73x35.png 73w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/6-Casper-Unboxing-Video-105x50.png 105w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/6-Casper-Unboxing-Video-740x353.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/6-Casper-Unboxing-Video-220x105.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/6-Casper-Unboxing-Video-385x183.png 385w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>No es sorpresa que 53.86% de todo el tráfico social de Casper venga de YouTube (y la mayor parte viene de los videos de sus <em>clientes</em>, no de sus propios videos).</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="259" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/7-Casper_s-Social-Traffic-1024x259.png" alt="7 Casper_s Social Traffic" class="wp-image-113765" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/7-Casper_s-Social-Traffic-1024x259.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/7-Casper_s-Social-Traffic-300x76.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/7-Casper_s-Social-Traffic-768x194.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/7-Casper_s-Social-Traffic-1536x388.png 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/7-Casper_s-Social-Traffic-380x96.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/7-Casper_s-Social-Traffic-600x152.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/7-Casper_s-Social-Traffic-760x192.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/7-Casper_s-Social-Traffic-1440x364.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/7-Casper_s-Social-Traffic-139x35.png 139w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/7-Casper_s-Social-Traffic-198x50.png 198w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/7-Casper_s-Social-Traffic-740x187.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/7-Casper_s-Social-Traffic-220x56.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/7-Casper_s-Social-Traffic-385x97.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/7-Casper_s-Social-Traffic.png 1999w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>Cuando reinventas una experiencia de compra, la gente presta atención.</p>



<div class="wp-block-group is-style-shadow-box has-sleek-light-grey-background-color has-background"><div class="wp-block-group__inner-container">
<p><strong>Elemento de acción</strong>: Pregúntate: “¿Puedo reinventar la experiencia de compra para mis clientes? ¿Puedo capitalizar una tendencia en crecimiento para ayudar a ofrecer esa experiencia? ¿Puedo hacer que cada etapa del ciclo de compra sea memorable y que valga la pena compartir?”.</p>
</div></div>



<h2 id="2"><strong>Estrategia #2: Crea una garantía insuperable</strong></h2>



<p>Imagina, por un momento, que estás en una tienda de mascotas y tu hijo te suplica que le des un cachorrito.&nbsp;</p>



<p>Sin saber si es una buena idea, le dices que no.&nbsp;</p>



<p>El vendedor, que ya conoce esta dinámica, te propone lo siguiente: “Llévate el cachorro a casa por un fin de semana. Si es demasiada responsabilidad, devuélvelo el lunes y te daré un reembolso completo, sin hacer preguntas”.</p>



<p>Esperando en secreto que tu hijo haya perdido el interés al terminar el fin de semana, aceptas llevarte el cachorro a casa. La mayor parte del tiempo, habrás estado en lo correcto. Tu hijo <em>sí</em> perdió el interés en el cachorro… pero tú te enamoraste. Para la noche del domingo, quieres más el cachorro de lo que lo quería tu hijo. Ding. Ding.</p>



<p>El cierre del cachorro, como se le conoce, es una de las técnicas de cierre de ventas más efectivas. Y, previsiblemente, una que Casper aprovecha en su marketing de forma notable con su garantía insuperable.</p>



<p>Casper ofrece para todos sus colchones un periodo de prueba gratuito libre de riesgos de 100 noches.</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="448" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/8-Casper_s-Guarantee-1024x448.png" alt="8 Casper_s Guarantee" class="wp-image-113769" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/8-Casper_s-Guarantee-1024x448.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/8-Casper_s-Guarantee-300x131.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/8-Casper_s-Guarantee-768x336.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/8-Casper_s-Guarantee-1536x672.png 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/8-Casper_s-Guarantee-380x166.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/8-Casper_s-Guarantee-600x263.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/8-Casper_s-Guarantee-760x333.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/8-Casper_s-Guarantee-1440x630.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/8-Casper_s-Guarantee-80x35.png 80w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/8-Casper_s-Guarantee-114x50.png 114w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/8-Casper_s-Guarantee-740x324.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/8-Casper_s-Guarantee-220x96.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/8-Casper_s-Guarantee-385x168.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/8-Casper_s-Guarantee.png 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>¿La promesa? Si decides que el colchón de Casper no es adecuado para ti, enviarán a un repartidor para que se lo lleve de tu casa. Se lo donarán a una beneficencia local o lo reciclarán. Lo mejor de todo es que ni siquiera tienes que tener la caja.</p>



<p>Casper no se enfoca solo en hacer dinero; se interesa en ayudar a las personas necesitadas y en hacer su parte para ayudar al ambiente. Esto resuena con los millennials, especialmente, quienes consideran a la beneficencia y el ambiente factores decisivos clave en sus decisiones de compra (ht: Rikke).</p>



<p>También existe un beneficio secundario de ofrecer una prueba gratuita de 100 noches. Casper sabe que una vez que el cliente hace del producto parte de su vida diaria, a sabiendas o no, es menos probable que lo regrese.</p>



<p>Como se dijo antes, la prueba gratuita de 100 noches de Casper no es algo que se menciona casualmente como una simple ocurrencia tardía (como, por ejemplo, en su página de pago). En vez de eso, es algo que está presente de forma consistente en cada etapa de su embudo (especialmente en los emails de recuperación del carrito de compras, cosa que discutiremos en la Parte 5: Estrategia #1).</p>



<div class="wp-block-group is-style-shadow-box has-sleek-light-grey-background-color has-background"><div class="wp-block-group__inner-container">
<p><strong>Elemento de acción</strong>: Probablemente ya tienes una garantía para tus productos, pero, ¿es insuperable? ¿Es una por la que tus clientes te adoran (y tus competidores te odian)? Si no es así, considera bajar la barrera para que tu oferta sea tan buena que los clientes potenciales no puedan ignorarla.&nbsp;</p>
</div></div>



<h2><strong>Parte 2: Marketing de contenido</strong></h2>



<p>Casper aprovecha tres arquetipos de contenido como parte de su estrategia, cada una con el objetivo de llevar a los clientes potenciales más adelante en el embudo de compra.&nbsp;</p>



<p>Como recordatorio, este es un ejemplo de un embudo, incluyendo ejemplos de arquetipos de contenido en cada etapa:</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="470" height="421" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/9-Purchase-Funnel.png" alt="9 Purchase Funnel" class="wp-image-113773" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/9-Purchase-Funnel.png 470w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/9-Purchase-Funnel-300x269.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/9-Purchase-Funnel-380x340.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/9-Purchase-Funnel-39x35.png 39w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/9-Purchase-Funnel-56x50.png 56w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/9-Purchase-Funnel-220x197.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/9-Purchase-Funnel-385x345.png 385w" sizes="(max-width: 470px) 100vw, 470px" /><figcaption>Fuente: <a href="http://cartina.se/guide-hur-jobba-med-content-marketing-har-ar-allt-du-behover-veta/tofu-mofu-bofu/">C</a><a href="http://cartina.se/guide-hur-jobba-med-content-marketing-har-ar-allt-du-behover-veta/tofu-mofu-bofu/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">artina</a></figcaption></figure></div>







<p>Demos un vistazo.</p>



<h2 id="3"><strong>Estrategia #3: Responde las preguntas de tu mercado meta (ToFu)</strong></h2>



<p>El blog de Casper, <a href="http://blog.casper.com/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener nofollow">Pillow Talk</a> (que se traduce como “Conversaciones de almohada”), aparece en la primera página de muchas palabras clave medium-tail, como “no puedo dormir” y “posiciones para dormir”. También aparece para búsquedas más generales, long-tail, como “qué haces cuando no puedes dormir” y “cómo dormirse más temprano”.</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="437" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/10-Casper_s-Organic-Keywords-1024x437.png" alt="10 Casper_s Organic Keywords" class="wp-image-113777" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/10-Casper_s-Organic-Keywords-1024x437.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/10-Casper_s-Organic-Keywords-300x128.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/10-Casper_s-Organic-Keywords-768x328.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/10-Casper_s-Organic-Keywords-380x162.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/10-Casper_s-Organic-Keywords-600x256.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/10-Casper_s-Organic-Keywords-760x324.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/10-Casper_s-Organic-Keywords-960x410.png 960w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/10-Casper_s-Organic-Keywords-82x35.png 82w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/10-Casper_s-Organic-Keywords-117x50.png 117w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/10-Casper_s-Organic-Keywords-740x316.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/10-Casper_s-Organic-Keywords-220x94.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/10-Casper_s-Organic-Keywords-385x164.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/10-Casper_s-Organic-Keywords.png 1395w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>Mucho de su contenido To-Fu es corto y humorístico, mientras que otro, como veremos en la Parte 3: Estrategia #2, es contenido bien investigado.</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="214" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Casper-Content-Example-1024x214.png" alt="Casper Content Example" class="wp-image-113950" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Casper-Content-Example-1024x214.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Casper-Content-Example-300x63.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Casper-Content-Example-768x160.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Casper-Content-Example-1536x320.png 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Casper-Content-Example-380x79.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Casper-Content-Example-600x125.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Casper-Content-Example-760x159.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Casper-Content-Example-1440x300.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Casper-Content-Example-168x35.png 168w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Casper-Content-Example-240x50.png 240w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Casper-Content-Example-740x154.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Casper-Content-Example-220x46.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Casper-Content-Example-385x80.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Casper-Content-Example.png 1999w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>Interesantemente, en vez de pedirte tu dirección de email en esas páginas, Casper te incentiva a contestar una encuesta sobre tus hábitos de sueño, ofreciéndote un descuento de $25 como recompensa.</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="640" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/11-Casper-Survey-Popup-1024x640.png" alt="11 Casper Survey Popup" class="wp-image-113781" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/11-Casper-Survey-Popup-1024x640.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/11-Casper-Survey-Popup-300x187.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/11-Casper-Survey-Popup-768x480.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/11-Casper-Survey-Popup-1536x960.png 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/11-Casper-Survey-Popup-380x237.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/11-Casper-Survey-Popup-600x375.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/11-Casper-Survey-Popup-760x475.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/11-Casper-Survey-Popup-1440x900.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/11-Casper-Survey-Popup-56x35.png 56w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/11-Casper-Survey-Popup-80x50.png 80w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/11-Casper-Survey-Popup-740x462.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/11-Casper-Survey-Popup-220x137.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/11-Casper-Survey-Popup-385x241.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/11-Casper-Survey-Popup.png 1999w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>En esta encuesta, te preguntan sobre tu posición preferida para dormir, tu rutina nocturna y preguntas demográficas generales de edad, ingresos, género y otras:</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="488" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/12-Preferred-Sleeping-Position-1024x488.png" alt="12 Preferred Sleeping Position" class="wp-image-113785" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/12-Preferred-Sleeping-Position-1024x488.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/12-Preferred-Sleeping-Position-300x143.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/12-Preferred-Sleeping-Position-768x366.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/12-Preferred-Sleeping-Position-1536x732.png 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/12-Preferred-Sleeping-Position-380x181.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/12-Preferred-Sleeping-Position-600x286.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/12-Preferred-Sleeping-Position-760x362.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/12-Preferred-Sleeping-Position-1440x687.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/12-Preferred-Sleeping-Position-73x35.png 73w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/12-Preferred-Sleeping-Position-105x50.png 105w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/12-Preferred-Sleeping-Position-740x353.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/12-Preferred-Sleeping-Position-220x105.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/12-Preferred-Sleeping-Position-385x184.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/12-Preferred-Sleeping-Position.png 1999w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>Al final de la encuesta te piden tu dirección de email, antes de ofrecer un código de cupón.&nbsp;</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="488" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/13-Casper_s-Survey-Confirmation-Page-1024x488.png" alt="13 Casper_s Survey Confirmation Page" class="wp-image-113789" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/13-Casper_s-Survey-Confirmation-Page-1024x488.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/13-Casper_s-Survey-Confirmation-Page-300x143.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/13-Casper_s-Survey-Confirmation-Page-768x366.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/13-Casper_s-Survey-Confirmation-Page-1536x732.png 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/13-Casper_s-Survey-Confirmation-Page-380x181.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/13-Casper_s-Survey-Confirmation-Page-600x286.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/13-Casper_s-Survey-Confirmation-Page-760x362.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/13-Casper_s-Survey-Confirmation-Page-1440x687.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/13-Casper_s-Survey-Confirmation-Page-73x35.png 73w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/13-Casper_s-Survey-Confirmation-Page-105x50.png 105w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/13-Casper_s-Survey-Confirmation-Page-740x353.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/13-Casper_s-Survey-Confirmation-Page-220x105.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/13-Casper_s-Survey-Confirmation-Page-385x184.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/13-Casper_s-Survey-Confirmation-Page.png 1999w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>Casper incluso monitorea cuántos visitantes hacen clic en “Comprar en Casper” después de completar la encuesta, para determinar si vale la pena continuar con la estrategia:</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="27" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/14-Promo-Code-Labs-1024x27.png" alt="14 Promo Code Labs" class="wp-image-113793" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/14-Promo-Code-Labs-1024x27.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/14-Promo-Code-Labs-300x8.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/14-Promo-Code-Labs-768x20.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/14-Promo-Code-Labs-1536x41.png 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/14-Promo-Code-Labs-380x10.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/14-Promo-Code-Labs-600x16.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/14-Promo-Code-Labs-760x20.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/14-Promo-Code-Labs-1440x38.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/14-Promo-Code-Labs-180x5.png 180w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/14-Promo-Code-Labs-250x7.png 250w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/14-Promo-Code-Labs-740x20.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/14-Promo-Code-Labs-220x6.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/14-Promo-Code-Labs-385x10.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/14-Promo-Code-Labs.png 1999w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>Y esto es inteligente, por tres razones:</p>



<ol><li>Responder a las preguntas más urgentes de sus compradores meta incrementa la huella orgánica de Casper en los SERP, y les posiciona como una autoridad en el mercado.</li><li>Encuestar a los visitantes que llegan por consultas específicas de búsqueda les da un grupo focal y feedbacks altamente específicos, lo que les permite mejorar su marketing.</li><li>Ofrecer un descuento, front-end, a un visitante que llegó por una búsqueda orgánica impulsa rápidamente a los compradores sin la necesidad de pagar por tráfico (más sobre esto en la Parte 4).&nbsp;</li></ol>



<div class="wp-block-group is-style-shadow-box has-sleek-light-grey-background-color has-background"><div class="wp-block-group__inner-container">
<p><strong>Elemento de acción</strong>: Usa sitios como Quora y Reddit, investiga las preguntas más apremiantes de tu mercado meta y crea contenido que responda esas preguntas. Para saber más sobre cómo hacer esto, paso a paso, <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/e-commerce-copywriting">lee este artículo</a>.</p>
</div></div>



<h2 id="4"><strong>Estrategia #4: Crea un recurso de comparación al cual acudir (MoFu)</strong></h2>



<p>Un obstáculo común para comprar algo, como un colchón, es no saber cuál es el adecuado para ti.</p>



<p>Como se mencionó antes, hay muchas cosas a considerar, como el tipo de colchón, su tamaño, su firmeza y más.&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>



<p>Casper ayuda a compradores potenciales a disipar la confusión con su <a href="https://casper.com/ca/en/mattress-size-comparison-guide/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener nofollow">guía de comparación de tamaño de colchones</a>.&nbsp;</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="576" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/15-Casper_s-Mattress-Comparison-Guide-1024x576.png" alt="15 Casper_s Mattress Comparison Guide" class="wp-image-113797" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/15-Casper_s-Mattress-Comparison-Guide-1024x576.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/15-Casper_s-Mattress-Comparison-Guide-300x169.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/15-Casper_s-Mattress-Comparison-Guide-768x432.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/15-Casper_s-Mattress-Comparison-Guide-1536x864.png 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/15-Casper_s-Mattress-Comparison-Guide-380x214.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/15-Casper_s-Mattress-Comparison-Guide-600x338.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/15-Casper_s-Mattress-Comparison-Guide-760x428.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/15-Casper_s-Mattress-Comparison-Guide-1440x810.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/15-Casper_s-Mattress-Comparison-Guide-62x35.png 62w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/15-Casper_s-Mattress-Comparison-Guide-89x50.png 89w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/15-Casper_s-Mattress-Comparison-Guide-740x416.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/15-Casper_s-Mattress-Comparison-Guide-220x124.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/15-Casper_s-Mattress-Comparison-Guide-385x217.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/15-Casper_s-Mattress-Comparison-Guide.png 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>Aunque no es muy larga, sí clasifica para cientos de palabras clave en la posición #1, incluyendo varias palabras clave long-tail, como “dimensiones de la cama tamaño king” y “dimensiones del colchón queen”.&nbsp;</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="374" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/16-Casper_s-Positions-in-The-SERPs-1024x374.png" alt="16 Casper_s Positions in The SERPs" class="wp-image-113801" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/16-Casper_s-Positions-in-The-SERPs-1024x374.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/16-Casper_s-Positions-in-The-SERPs-300x110.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/16-Casper_s-Positions-in-The-SERPs-768x281.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/16-Casper_s-Positions-in-The-SERPs-380x139.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/16-Casper_s-Positions-in-The-SERPs-600x219.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/16-Casper_s-Positions-in-The-SERPs-760x278.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/16-Casper_s-Positions-in-The-SERPs-96x35.png 96w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/16-Casper_s-Positions-in-The-SERPs-137x50.png 137w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/16-Casper_s-Positions-in-The-SERPs-740x271.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/16-Casper_s-Positions-in-The-SERPs-220x80.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/16-Casper_s-Positions-in-The-SERPs-385x141.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/16-Casper_s-Positions-in-The-SERPs.png 1395w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>Y, para palabras claves con las que no clasifica en la posición #1, se clasifica en los featured snippets (fragmentos destacados, también conocidos como Posición #0).&nbsp;</p>



<p>Por ejemplo, para “dimensiones de la cama tamaño queen en pies”, se clasifican en la posición #6 (al momento de escribir este artículo), pero clasifican para un featured snippet, robándose <a href="https://ahrefs.com/blog/find-featured-snippets/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener nofollow">8.6% de todos los clics</a> en el proceso.</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="623" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/17-Queen-Size-Bed-Dimensions-in-Feet-1024x623.png" alt="17 Queen Size Bed Dimensions in Feet" class="wp-image-113805" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/17-Queen-Size-Bed-Dimensions-in-Feet-1024x623.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/17-Queen-Size-Bed-Dimensions-in-Feet-300x183.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/17-Queen-Size-Bed-Dimensions-in-Feet-768x467.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/17-Queen-Size-Bed-Dimensions-in-Feet-380x231.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/17-Queen-Size-Bed-Dimensions-in-Feet-600x365.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/17-Queen-Size-Bed-Dimensions-in-Feet-760x462.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/17-Queen-Size-Bed-Dimensions-in-Feet-58x35.png 58w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/17-Queen-Size-Bed-Dimensions-in-Feet-82x50.png 82w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/17-Queen-Size-Bed-Dimensions-in-Feet-740x450.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/17-Queen-Size-Bed-Dimensions-in-Feet-220x134.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/17-Queen-Size-Bed-Dimensions-in-Feet-385x234.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/17-Queen-Size-Bed-Dimensions-in-Feet.png 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>Lo interesante es que, en vez de pedirte tu feedback en esta página, como lo hacen con su contenido To-Fu, Casper te invita a entrar en una competencia. </p>


