<div style="height:40px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>







<p>Es algo inteligente. Es más probable que un visitante que compara tamaños de colchones avance en el camino del comprador, que alguien que está buscando medicamentos para dormir. Así que Casper pide el email, en vez de un feedback, y presenta sus productos en sus emails de presentación (más de esto en la Parte 5).</p>



<div class="wp-block-group is-style-shadow-box has-sleek-light-grey-background-color has-background"><div class="wp-block-group__inner-container">
<p><strong>Elemento de acción</strong>: Si vendes diferentes tipos de productos (ej., cosméticos como bases), crea una guía comparativa que ayude a los compradores a encontrar el producto adecuado para cada quién. Bono, si puedes posicionarla bien en los SERP.</p>
</div></div>



<h2 id="5"><strong>Estrategia #5: Muestra todas las reseñas en un solo lugar (BoFu)</strong></h2>



<p>Sabes lo importante que es usar testimonios de clientes para ayudar a convencer a clientes potenciales. Pero, ¿los estás mostrando de la mejor forma?</p>



<p>Conociendo la importancia de las reseñas en un mercado competitivo, Casper muestra todas sus reseñas en una página en su sitio.</p>



<p>Primero, muestran reseñas escritas por sus clientes, incluyendo el nombre de la persona, de dónde es y cómo califican a Casper.</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="532" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/19-Casper_s-Reviews-1024x532.png" alt="19 Casper_s Reviews" class="wp-image-113813" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/19-Casper_s-Reviews-1024x532.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/19-Casper_s-Reviews-300x156.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/19-Casper_s-Reviews-768x399.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/19-Casper_s-Reviews-380x198.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/19-Casper_s-Reviews-600x312.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/19-Casper_s-Reviews-760x395.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/19-Casper_s-Reviews-67x35.png 67w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/19-Casper_s-Reviews-96x50.png 96w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/19-Casper_s-Reviews-740x385.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/19-Casper_s-Reviews-220x114.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/19-Casper_s-Reviews-385x200.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/19-Casper_s-Reviews.png 1250w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>(Casper es 100% transparente aquí. Si haces clic en “Ver todas las reseñas”, podrás leer todo lo que sus clientes dicen sobre ellos, incluyendo los insatisfechos).</p>



<p>Debajo de las reseñas puedes leer tuits de los clientes, lo que le añade más legitimidad a sus reseñas.&nbsp;</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="393" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/20-Casper-Tweet-Testimonial-1024x393.png" alt="20 Casper Tweet Testimonial" class="wp-image-113817" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/20-Casper-Tweet-Testimonial-1024x393.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/20-Casper-Tweet-Testimonial-300x115.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/20-Casper-Tweet-Testimonial-768x294.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/20-Casper-Tweet-Testimonial-380x146.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/20-Casper-Tweet-Testimonial-600x230.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/20-Casper-Tweet-Testimonial-760x291.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/20-Casper-Tweet-Testimonial-91x35.png 91w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/20-Casper-Tweet-Testimonial-130x50.png 130w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/20-Casper-Tweet-Testimonial-740x284.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/20-Casper-Tweet-Testimonial-220x84.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/20-Casper-Tweet-Testimonial-385x148.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/20-Casper-Tweet-Testimonial.png 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>Finalmente, Casper añade la tercera capa de prueba social: insignias de medios y menciones de prensa.</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="646" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/21-Casper_s-Media-Mentions-1024x646.png" alt="21 Casper_s Media Mentions" class="wp-image-113821" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/21-Casper_s-Media-Mentions-1024x646.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/21-Casper_s-Media-Mentions-300x189.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/21-Casper_s-Media-Mentions-768x485.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/21-Casper_s-Media-Mentions-1536x969.png 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/21-Casper_s-Media-Mentions-380x240.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/21-Casper_s-Media-Mentions-600x379.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/21-Casper_s-Media-Mentions-760x479.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/21-Casper_s-Media-Mentions-1440x909.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/21-Casper_s-Media-Mentions-55x35.png 55w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/21-Casper_s-Media-Mentions-79x50.png 79w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/21-Casper_s-Media-Mentions-740x467.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/21-Casper_s-Media-Mentions-220x139.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/21-Casper_s-Media-Mentions-385x243.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/21-Casper_s-Media-Mentions.png 1585w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>Hay una razón por la cual Casper se esfuerza tanto en optimizar su página de reseñas, y la discutiremos en la Parte 5: Estrategia #2.</p>



<div class="wp-block-group is-style-shadow-box has-sleek-light-grey-background-color has-background"><div class="wp-block-group__inner-container">
<p><strong>Elemento de acción: </strong>Es común que las tiendas online tengan sus reseñas en sitios de terceros. Pero eso no siempre significa que sea la mejor práctica. Toma tus mejores reseñas y tenlas en tu sitio, para que tengas más control sobre la forma en que promocionas tu negocio.&nbsp;</p>
</div></div>



<h2><strong>Parte 3: Link Building</strong></h2>



<p>Al momento de escribir este artículo, Casper tenía 148k backlinks de 5.54 dominios de referencia.</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="152" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/22-Casper_s-Backlinks-1024x152.png" alt="22 Casper_s Backlinks" class="wp-image-113825" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/22-Casper_s-Backlinks-1024x152.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/22-Casper_s-Backlinks-300x44.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/22-Casper_s-Backlinks-768x114.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/22-Casper_s-Backlinks-1536x227.png 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/22-Casper_s-Backlinks-380x56.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/22-Casper_s-Backlinks-600x89.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/22-Casper_s-Backlinks-760x113.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/22-Casper_s-Backlinks-1440x213.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/22-Casper_s-Backlinks-180x27.png 180w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/22-Casper_s-Backlinks-250x37.png 250w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/22-Casper_s-Backlinks-740x110.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/22-Casper_s-Backlinks-220x33.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/22-Casper_s-Backlinks-385x57.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/22-Casper_s-Backlinks.png 1999w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>Es impresionante, pero a menos que tengas un presupuesto de marketing multimillonario, pocas de sus estrategias de link building (creación de enlaces) son replicables (si tienes curiosidad, he incluido mis tres favoritas en el recurso bono).</p>



<p>Así que, en vez de explorar lo que no se puede replicar, quiero mostrarte tres formas no convencionales en las que Casper crea enlaces y cómo tú también puedes hacerlo.&nbsp;</p>



<h2 id="6"><strong>Estrategia #6: Crea enlaces white hat educativos con “El método CSD”&nbsp;</strong></h2>



<p>Si sabes algo acerca del link building, sabes que obtener enlaces .edu es lo mejor que puedes hacer. Aprueban MUCHÍSIMOS PageRank, pero son difíciles de adquirir. A menos, por supuesto, que tengas un ángulo único&#8230;</p>



<p>Echa un vistazo a los dominios de referencia de Casper.</p>



<p>Si refinamos la búsqueda, podemos ver que han desarrollado doce enlaces .edu do-follow, usando lo que yo llamo estrategia del descuento de estudiante universitario (CSD, por sus siglas en inglés.&nbsp;</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="536" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/23-Education-Links-to-Casper-1024x536.png" alt="23 Education Links to Casper" class="wp-image-113829" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/23-Education-Links-to-Casper-1024x536.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/23-Education-Links-to-Casper-300x157.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/23-Education-Links-to-Casper-768x402.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/23-Education-Links-to-Casper-1536x804.png 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/23-Education-Links-to-Casper-380x199.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/23-Education-Links-to-Casper-600x314.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/23-Education-Links-to-Casper-760x398.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/23-Education-Links-to-Casper-1440x754.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/23-Education-Links-to-Casper-67x35.png 67w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/23-Education-Links-to-Casper-95x50.png 95w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/23-Education-Links-to-Casper-740x388.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/23-Education-Links-to-Casper-220x115.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/23-Education-Links-to-Casper-385x202.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wp