<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="640" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/26-Link-from-SUNY-1024x640.png" alt="26 Link from SUNY" class="wp-image-113841" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/26-Link-from-SUNY-1024x640.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/26-Link-from-SUNY-300x187.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/26-Link-from-SUNY-768x480.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/26-Link-from-SUNY-1536x960.png 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/26-Link-from-SUNY-380x237.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/26-Link-from-SUNY-600x375.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/26-Link-from-SUNY-760x475.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/26-Link-from-SUNY-1440x900.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/26-Link-from-SUNY-56x35.png 56w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/26-Link-from-SUNY-80x50.png 80w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/26-Link-from-SUNY-740x462.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/26-Link-from-SUNY-220x137.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/26-Link-from-SUNY-385x241.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/26-Link-from-SUNY.png 1999w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>Si bajas en la página, verás que también tienen un descuento en colchones Casper.</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="274" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/27-Casper-Discount-Code-2-1024x274.png" alt="27 Casper Discount Code 2" class="wp-image-113845" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/27-Casper-Discount-Code-2-1024x274.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/27-Casper-Discount-Code-2-300x80.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/27-Casper-Discount-Code-2-768x205.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/27-Casper-Discount-Code-2-1536x410.png 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/27-Casper-Discount-Code-2-380x102.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/27-Casper-Discount-Code-2-600x160.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/27-Casper-Discount-Code-2-760x203.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/27-Casper-Discount-Code-2-1440x385.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/27-Casper-Discount-Code-2-131x35.png 131w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/27-Casper-Discount-Code-2-187x50.png 187w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/27-Casper-Discount-Code-2-740x198.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/27-Casper-Discount-Code-2-220x59.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/27-Casper-Discount-Code-2-385x103.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/27-Casper-Discount-Code-2.png 1999w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>Si bien es imposible saber si Casper buscó activamente estos links y otros, ciertamente es altamente probable, dada la frecuencia de estos tipos de enlaces y los PageRank que aprueban.&nbsp;</p>



<div class="wp-block-group is-style-shadow-box has-sleek-light-grey-background-color has-background"><div class="wp-block-group__inner-container">
<p><strong>Elemento de acción</strong>: Es fácil asumir que la creación de enlaces, como los mencionados anteriormente, es imposible. Pero muchos sitios, como CSUN, tienen un formulario en el que puedes enviar tus propios descuentos. Pregúntate: “¿A quién más puedo servir?”. Entonces, considera dónde pasa su tiempo ese mercado meta y ponte en contacto con los sitios adecuados.</p>
</div></div>



<h2 id="7"><strong>Estrategia #7: Publica investigación original (y conviértete en una autoridad en tu mercado)</strong></h2>



<p>En la Sección #2 discutimos los tres arquetipos de contenido que Casper usa para generar tráfico de búsqueda. También aprendiste que uno de esos arquetipos es contenido que responda las preguntas de tu mercado meta.</p>



<p>Casper hace un trabajo excelente con eso. Pero, a veces, responder una pregunta va más allá de dar una opinión. En realidad, para convertirte en una autoridad en un tema, a menudo debes citar o, mejor aún, publicar investigación <em>original</em>.&nbsp;</p>



<p>Mira, por ejemplo, este post de Casper, “<a href="https://casper.com/ca/en/faqs/ca-the-mattress/how-often-should-i-replace-my-mattress/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener nofollow">¿Cuán a menudo debo reemplazar mi colchón?</a>”.</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="470" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/28-How-Often-Should-I-Replace-My-Mattress-1024x470.png" alt="28 How Often Should I Replace My Mattress" class="wp-image-113849" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/28-How-Often-Should-I-Replace-My-Mattress-1024x470.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/28-How-Often-Should-I-Replace-My-Mattress-300x138.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/28-How-Often-Should-I-Replace-My-Mattress-768x352.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/28-How-Often-Should-I-Replace-My-Mattress-1536x705.png 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/28-How-Often-Should-I-Replace-My-Mattress-380x174.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/28-How-Often-Should-I-Replace-My-Mattress-600x275.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/28-How-Often-Should-I-Replace-My-Mattress-760x349.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/28-How-Often-Should-I-Replace-My-Mattress-1440x661.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/28-How-Often-Should-I-Replace-My-Mattress-76x35.png 76w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/28-How-Often-Should-I-Replace-My-Mattress-109x50.png 109w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/28-How-Often-Should-I-Replace-My-Mattress-740x339.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/28-How-Often-Should-I-Replace-My-Mattress-220x101.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/28-How-Often-Should-I-Replace-My-Mattress-385x177.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/28-How-Often-Should-I-Replace-My-Mattress.png 1999w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>Allí, Casper desmiente un mito de la industria sobre cuán a menudo deberías cambiar tu colchón.&nbsp;</p>



<p>En vez de citar investigaciones de otras personas, usaron sus propios hallazgos al investigar sobre sus propios colchones, y aclararon las cosas.</p>



<p>Esta página en sus Preguntas Frecuentes obtuvo un buen enlace DR90 de <a href="https://www.healthline.com/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener nofollow">Healthline</a>, lo cual solo demuestra:&nbsp;</p>



<p><em>El contenido no siempre necesita ser publicado en un blog para que adquiera links.</em>&nbsp;</p>



<div class="wp-block-group is-style-shadow-box has-sleek-light-grey-background-color has-background"><div class="wp-block-group__inner-container">
<p><strong>Elemento de acción</strong>: Si estás creando contenido para tu sitio, considera publicar una investigación original (incluso si es un metaanálisis de otros estudios). Sí, toma tiempo. Pero también puede ser un activo para que sitios en tu mercado se enlacen.</p>
</div></div>



<h2 id="8"><strong>Estrategia #8: Usa el “creador de backlink de ‘lo mejor de’” (con un giro)</strong></h2>



<p>Una de las formas más rápidas y fáciles para que los comerciantes online creen links es aparecer en contenido “lo mejor de”: contenido que cura lo mejor de lo mejor de un nicho (yo lo llamo “<a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/harrys-marketing" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">creador de backlink de ‘lo mejor de’</a>”).</p>



<p>Por ejemplo, Casper ha creado varios enlaces de autoridad de alto dominio logrando aparecer en contenido “mejores ideas de [palabra clave]”, como “mejores ideas de regalos de boda”.</p>



<p>De hecho, Casper ha adquirido varios enlaces do-follow de varios sitios de alta autoridad como <a href="https://www.theknot.com/content/top-40-registry-picks" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener nofollow">The Knot</a> (DR:90) y <a href="https://www.brides.com/story/wedding-registry-splurges-and-group-gifts" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener nofollow">Brides</a> (DR:82) usando esta estrategia.&nbsp;</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="230" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/29-Link-from-Brides-1024x230.png" alt="29 Link from Brides" class="wp-image-113853" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/29-Link-from-Brides-1024x230.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/29-Link-from-Brides-300x68.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/29-Link-from-Brides-768x173.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/29-Link-from-Brides-1536x346.png 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/29-Link-from-Brides-380x86.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/29-Link-from-Brides-600x135.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/29-Link-from-Brides-760x171.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/29-Link-from-Brides-1440x324.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/29-Link-from-Brides-156x35.png 156w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/29-Link-from-Brides-222x50.png 222w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/29-Link-from-Brides-740x167.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/29-Link-from-Brides-220x50.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/29-Link-from-Brides-385x87.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/29-Link-from-Brides.png 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>Ahora, aquí es donde viene un giro interesante.</p>



<p><a href="https://heavy.com/social/2016/03/top-best-bridal-shower-gift-ideas-gifts-wedding-bride-unique/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener nofollow">Heavy</a>, un sitio de noticias e información, también presenta a Casper en un artículo de “lo mejor de” sobre “las principales ideas de regalo para una despedida de soltera”.</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="499" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/30-Top-Bridal-Shower-Gift-Ideas-1024x499.png" alt="30 Top Bridal Shower Gift Ideas" class="wp-image-113857" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/30-Top-Bridal-Shower-Gift-Ideas-1024x499.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/30-Top-Bridal-Shower-Gift-Ideas-300x146.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/30-Top-Bridal-Shower-Gift-Ideas-768x374.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/30-Top-Bridal-Shower-Gift-Ideas-1536x749.png 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/30-Top-Bridal-Shower-Gift-Ideas-380x185.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/30-Top-Bridal-Shower-Gift-Ideas-600x293.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/30-Top-Bridal-Shower-Gift-Ideas-760x371.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/30-Top-Bridal-Shower-Gift-Ideas-1440x702.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/30-Top-Bridal-Shower-Gift-Ideas-72x35.png 72w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/30-Top-Bridal-Shower-Gift-Ideas-103x50.png 103w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/30-Top-Bridal-Shower-Gift-Ideas-740x361.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/30-Top-Bridal-Shower-Gift-Ideas-220x107.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/30-Top-Bridal-Shower-Gift-Ideas-385x188.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/30-Top-Bridal-Shower-Gift-Ideas.png 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>Pero, al inspeccionar de cerca, es realmente un link de afiliado.</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="25" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/31-Heavy-Affiliate-Link-1024x25.png" alt="31 Heavy Affiliate Link" class="wp-image-113861" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/31-Heavy-Affiliate-Link-1024x25.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/31-Heavy-Affiliate-Link-300x7.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/31-Heavy-Affiliate-Link-768x19.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/31-Heavy-Affiliate-Link-380x9.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/31-Heavy-Affiliate-Link-600x15.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/31-Heavy-Affiliate-Link-760x19.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/31-Heavy-Affiliate-Link-1440x35.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/31-Heavy-Affiliate-Link-180x4.png 180w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/31-Heavy-Affiliate-Link-250x6.png 250w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/31-Heavy-Affiliate-Link-740x18.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/31-Heavy-Affiliate-Link-220x5.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/31-Heavy-Affiliate-Link-385x9.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/31-Heavy-Affiliate-Link.png 1475w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>Si bien es altamente improbable que un sitio como Casper haya pedido aparecer en un artículo como este, sí es probable que sitios como Heavy estén más dispuestos a enlazarse a un producto si existe la oportunidad de ganar una comisión en el backend (así que, si no tienes un programa de afiliados para tus productos, podría valer la pena que lo pienses).</p>



<p>La mejor parte de aparecer en un contenido “lo mejor de”, por supuesto, es que es escalable.&nbsp;</p>



<p>Usando una herramienta como Ahrefs, puedes entrar al dominio de un competidor y hacer clic en “Dominios de referencia &gt; Backlinks” para ver el tipo de contenido en el que aparece. Entonces, puedes comenzar a buscar sitios similares (para saber más acerca de cómo hacer un análisis competitivo, <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/competitive-analysis" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">lee esta guía exhaustiva</a>).&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>



<div class="wp-block-group is-style-shadow-box has-sleek-light-grey-background-color has-background"><div class="wp-block-group__inner-container">
<p><strong>Elemento de acción</strong>: El creador de backlink de “lo mejor de” es una estrategia extremadamente buena si vendes productos que son buenas ideas de regalo. Usar operadores de búsqueda, como “los mejores regalos de [palabra clave]” “regalos de [palabra clave] para [género]”, te permite identificar sitios que pudieran incluir tu oferta. Entonces, contáctalos. Sí, toma tiempo. Pero es una grandiosa estrategia de link building para e-commerce.</p>
</div></div>



<h2><strong>Parte 4: Adquisición paga</strong></h2>



<p>Como muchas compañías multimillonarias, Casper invierte una fortuna en publicidad paga.</p>



<p>De hecho, al momento de escribir esto, su presupuesto mensual estimado solo para Google Adwords, era de $128,000 (fuente: <a href="https://www.similarweb.com/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener nofollow">SimilarWeb</a>).</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="398" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/32-Casper_s-Paid-Search-1024x398.png" alt="32 Casper_s Paid Search" class="wp-image-113865" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/32-Casper_s-Paid-Search-1024x398.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/32-Casper_s-Paid-Search-300x117.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/32-Casper_s-Paid-Search-768x299.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/32-Casper_s-Paid-Search-1536x597.png 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/32-Casper_s-Paid-Search-380x148.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/32-Casper_s-Paid-Search-600x233.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/32-Casper_s-Paid-Search-760x295.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/32-Casper_s-Paid-Search-1440x560.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/32-Casper_s-Paid-Search-90x35.png 90w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/32-Casper_s-Paid-Search-129x50.png 129w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/32-Casper_s-Paid-Search-740x288.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/32-Casper_s-Paid-Search-220x86.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/32-Casper_s-Paid-Search-385x150.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/32-Casper_s-Paid-Search.png 1999w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>Pero eso no significa que su estrategia no pueda ser adaptada a una escala más pequeña.</p>



<p>Estas son mis tres estrategias favoritas que encontré mientras investigaba.</p>



<h2 id="9"><strong>Estrategia #9: Traduce tus ads para captar nuevos mercados</strong></h2>



<p>Un buen marketero sabe qué países representan el mayor tráfico en su sitio.</p>



<p>Casper no es la excepción.</p>



<p>Usando una herramienta como <a href="http://similarweb.com/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener nofollow">SimilarWeb</a>, podemos ver que la mayoría del tráfico de Casper viene de Estados Unidos, Reino Unido, Canadá, Francia y Alemania.&nbsp;</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="493" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/33-Casper_s-Traffic-by-Countries-1024x493.png" alt="33 Casper_s Traffic by Countries" class="wp-image-113869" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/33-Casper_s-Traffic-by-Countries-1024x493.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/33-Casper_s-Traffic-by-Countries-300x144.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/33-Casper_s-Traffic-by-Countries-768x370.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/33-Casper_s-Traffic-by-Countries-1536x739.png 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/33-Casper_s-Traffic-by-Countries-380x183.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/33-Casper_s-Traffic-by-Countries-600x289.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/33-Casper_s-Traffic-by-Countries-760x366.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/33-Casper_s-Traffic-by-Countries-1440x693.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/33-Casper_s-Traffic-by-Countries-73x35.png 73w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/33-Casper_s-Traffic-by-Countries-104x50.png 104w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/33-Casper_s-Traffic-by-Countries-740x356.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/33-Casper_s-Traffic-by-Countries-220x106.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/33-Casper_s-Traffic-by-Countries-385x185.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/33-Casper_s-Traffic-by-Countries.png 1999w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>Entonces, tiene sentido que Casper cree publicidad en inglés para sus usuarios en Estados Unidos, Reino Unido y Canadá. Después de todo, el inglés es el idioma nativo de los Estados Unidos y el Reino Unido (y del 56.9% de Canadá).&nbsp;</p>



<p>Pero, ¿qué pasa con los países con Francia y Alemania, en los que el inglés no es su idioma principal?</p>



<p>Casper hace crecer su cuota del mercado en otros países traduciendo sus ads al idioma principal del país meta.</p>



<p>Mira, por ejemplo, el siguiente display ad, que les aparece a los visitantes alemanes que ya habían visitado el sitio de Casper.</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="728" height="90" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/34-Casper_s-German-Display-Ad.png" alt="34 Casper_s German Display Ad" class="wp-image-113873" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/34-Casper_s-German-Display-Ad.png 728w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/34-Casper_s-German-Display-Ad-300x37.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/34-Casper_s-German-Display-Ad-380x47.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/34-Casper_s-German-Display-Ad-600x74.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/34-Casper_s-German-Display-Ad-180x22.png 180w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/34-Casper_s-German-Display-Ad-250x31.png 250w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/34-Casper_s-German-Display-Ad-220x27.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/34-Casper_s-German-Display-Ad-385x48.png 385w" sizes="(max-width: 728px) 100vw, 728px" /></figure></div>



<p>Cuando les hacen clic, los usuarios son llevados a una página de aterrizaje, con textos y soporte al cliente en alemán.</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="491" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/35-Casper_s-German-Landing-Page-1024x491.png" alt="35 Casper_s German Landing Page" class="wp-image-113877" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/35-Casper_s-German-Landing-Page-1024x491.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/35-Casper_s-German-Landing-Page-300x144.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/35-Casper_s-German-Landing-Page-768x368.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/35-Casper_s-German-Landing-Page-1536x736.png 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/35-Casper_s-German-Landing-Page-380x182.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/35-Casper_s-German-Landing-Page-600x288.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/35-Casper_s-German-Landing-Page-760x364.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/35-Casper_s-German-Landing-Page-1440x690.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/35-Casper_s-German-Landing-Page-73x35.png 73w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/35-Casper_s-German-Landing-Page-104x50.png 104w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/35-Casper_s-German-Landing-Page-740x355.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/35-Casper_s-German-Landing-Page-220x105.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/35-Casper_s-German-Landing-Page-385x185.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/35-Casper_s-German-Landing-Page.png 1999w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>Si intentas irte, Casper te muestra un <a href="https://sleeknote.com/collect-email-addresses?ref=casper-marketing" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">popup de intención de salida</a> que te pide tu dirección de email.</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="767" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/36-Casper_s-German-Exit-Intent-Popup-1024x767.png" alt="36 Casper_s German Exit Intent Popup" class="wp-image-113882" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/36-Casper_s-German-Exit-Intent-Popup-1024x767.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/36-Casper_s-German-Exit-Intent-Popup-300x225.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/36-Casper_s-German-Exit-Intent-Popup-768x575.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/36-Casper_s-German-Exit-Intent-Popup-380x285.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/36-Casper_s-German-Exit-Intent-Popup-600x449.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/36-Casper_s-German-Exit-Intent-Popup-760x569.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/36-Casper_s-German-Exit-Intent-Popup-1440x1079.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/36-Casper_s-German-Exit-Intent-Popup-47x35.png 47w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/36-Casper_s-German-Exit-Intent-Popup-67x50.png 67w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/36-Casper_s-German-Exit-Intent-Popup-654x490.png 654w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/36-Casper_s-German-Exit-Intent-Popup-220x165.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/36-Casper_s-German-Exit-Intent-Popup-385x288.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/36-Casper_s-German-Exit-Intent-Popup.png 1455w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>En español, dice:</p>



<p>“Pronto haremos realidad uno de tus sueños. Regístrate y nunca ‘te duermas’ ante las noticias, productos y descuentos de Casper”.</p>



<p>Esta estrategia funciona bien por tres razones:</p>



<ol><li>Traducir un ad copy al idioma del mercado meta personaliza tu marketing.&nbsp;</li><li>Ofrecer soporte al cliente ayuda a los lectores a superar sus objeciones a comprar (más sobre esto en la Estrategia #12).</li><li>Captar las direcciones de email de los visitantes que abandonan tu sitio te da una oportunidad de ejecutar un remarketing usando otro medio (como el email).&nbsp;&nbsp;</li></ol>



<div class="wp-block-group is-style-shadow-box has-sleek-light-grey-background-color has-background"><div class="wp-block-group__inner-container">
<p><strong>Elemento de acción:</strong> Inicia sesión en Google Analytics y haz clic en “Audiencia &gt; Resumen &gt; País” para identificar tu audiencia por país. Luego, considera traducir tu ad copy al idioma nativo de uno o más de esos países.</p>
</div></div>



<div class="wp-block-group is-style-shadow-box has-sleek-grey-background-color has-background"><div class="wp-block-group__inner-container">
