<h2 id="10"><strong>Estrategia #10: Prueba este truco poco conocido para monopolizar tus ads de búsqueda</strong></h2>



<p>Si estás usando ads de búsqueda de Google para hacer crecer tu negocio, sabes que no puedes tener más de un ad de búsqueda que envíen a los visitantes al mismo sitio al mismo tiempo.&nbsp;</p>



<p>Pero eso no ha impedido que Casper monopolice sus palabras claves más rentables.</p>



<p>Mira, por ejemplo, “reseñas de colchones casper”, una consulta de búsqueda que discutimos antes.</p>



<p>Esto es lo que veo cuando escribo en Google ese término. ¿Notas algo interesante?</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="375" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/37-Casper_s-Google-Search-Ads-1024x375.png" alt="37 Casper_s Google Search Ads" class="wp-image-113886" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/37-Casper_s-Google-Search-Ads-1024x375.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/37-Casper_s-Google-Search-Ads-300x110.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/37-Casper_s-Google-Search-Ads-768x282.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/37-Casper_s-Google-Search-Ads-380x139.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/37-Casper_s-Google-Search-Ads-600x220.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/37-Casper_s-Google-Search-Ads-760x279.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/37-Casper_s-Google-Search-Ads-95x35.png 95w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/37-Casper_s-Google-Search-Ads-136x50.png 136w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/37-Casper_s-Google-Search-Ads-740x271.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/37-Casper_s-Google-Search-Ads-220x81.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/37-Casper_s-Google-Search-Ads-385x141.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/37-Casper_s-Google-Search-Ads.png 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>Casper domina tres de cuatro de los anuncios, dirigiendo a los visitantes a Amazon, Google Reviews y, por supuesto, su sitio. Todos son tiendas online que venden sus productos. Además, tienen un ad de Google Shopping a la derecha, haciendo casi imposible el ignorarlos.</p>



<p>Bastante listos, ¿verdad?</p>



<div class="wp-block-group is-style-shadow-box has-sleek-light-grey-background-color has-background"><div class="wp-block-group__inner-container">
<p><strong>Elemento de acción</strong>: Tienes razón. Esta estrategia es avanzada. Pero si puedes hacerla, y tus productos están disponibles en otros sitios, considera enviarles visitantes más allá de tu propio sitio.</p>
</div></div>



<h2 id="11"><strong>Estrategia #11: Combina publicidad y remarketing para obtener más leads para tu tienda online</strong></h2>



<p>Probablemente has experimentado con Facebook Advertising.&nbsp;</p>



<p>Y, si es así, es probable que hayas experimentado con el remarketing usando publicidad nativa.&nbsp;</p>



<p>Pero, ¿has probado ambos simultáneamente?</p>



<p>Casper sí. De hecho, es algo que hacen para ganar nuevos clientes.</p>



<p>Así es como funciona.&nbsp;</p>



<p>Primero, Casper publicita su marca a nuevas audiencias usando Facebook Ad.</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="751" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/38-Casper-Facebook-Ad-1024x751.png" alt="38 Casper Facebook Ad" class="wp-image-113890" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/38-Casper-Facebook-Ad-1024x751.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/38-Casper-Facebook-Ad-300x220.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/38-Casper-Facebook-Ad-768x563.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/38-Casper-Facebook-Ad-380x279.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/38-Casper-Facebook-Ad-600x440.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/38-Casper-Facebook-Ad-760x557.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/38-Casper-Facebook-Ad-1440x1056.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/38-Casper-Facebook-Ad-48x35.png 48w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/38-Casper-Facebook-Ad-68x50.png 68w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/38-Casper-Facebook-Ad-668x490.png 668w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/38-Casper-Facebook-Ad-220x161.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/38-Casper-Facebook-Ad-385x282.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/38-Casper-Facebook-Ad.png 1480w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>Con esto, incitan a los usuarios a hacer clic usando una brecha de curiosidad (“¿Qué es el fenómeno social del unboxing, y por qué está apoderándose de internet?”).</p>



<p>Desde allí, Casper envía a los usuarios a <a href="https://www.cbsnews.com/news/casper-the-warby-parker-of-mattresses/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener nofollow">un artículo de CBS</a> que alaba el posicionamiento de su marca.&nbsp;</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="488" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/39-How-a-Mattress-Company-Gains-an-Online-Following-1024x488.png" alt="39 How a Mattress Company Gains an Online Following" class="wp-image-113894" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/39-How-a-Mattress-Company-Gains-an-Online-Following-1024x488.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/39-How-a-Mattress-Company-Gains-an-Online-Following-300x143.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/39-How-a-Mattress-Company-Gains-an-Online-Following-768x366.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/39-How-a-Mattress-Company-Gains-an-Online-Following-1536x732.png 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/39-How-a-Mattress-Company-Gains-an-Online-Following-380x181.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/39-How-a-Mattress-Company-Gains-an-Online-Following-600x286.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/39-How-a-Mattress-Company-Gains-an-Online-Following-760x362.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/39-How-a-Mattress-Company-Gains-an-Online-Following-1440x687.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/39-How-a-Mattress-Company-Gains-an-Online-Following-73x35.png 73w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/39-How-a-Mattress-Company-Gains-an-Online-Following-105x50.png 105w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/39-How-a-Mattress-Company-Gains-an-Online-Following-740x353.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/39-How-a-Mattress-Company-Gains-an-Online-Following-220x105.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/39-How-a-Mattress-Company-Gains-an-Online-Following-385x184.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/39-How-a-Mattress-Company-Gains-an-Online-Following.png 1999w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>Ahora, quizás te preguntes: “¿Cuál es el punto de llevar tráfico al sitio de un tercero sin un llamado a la acción, además de desarrollar prueba social?”.</p>



<p>Si te hiciste esa pregunta, pues yo también reflexioné sobre eso.</p>



<p>Hasta que bajé al final de la página…</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="503" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/40-Casper_s-Native-Ad-1024x503.png" alt="40 Casper_s Native Ad" class="wp-image-113898" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/40-Casper_s-Native-Ad-1024x503.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/40-Casper_s-Native-Ad-300x147.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/40-Casper_s-Native-Ad-768x377.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/40-Casper_s-Native-Ad-1536x755.png 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/40-Casper_s-Native-Ad-380x187.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/40-Casper_s-Native-Ad-600x295.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/40-Casper_s-Native-Ad-760x373.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/40-Casper_s-Native-Ad-1440x707.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/40-Casper_s-Native-Ad-71x35.png 71w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/40-Casper_s-Native-Ad-102x50.png 102w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/40-Casper_s-Native-Ad-740x364.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/40-Casper_s-Native-Ad-220x108.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/40-Casper_s-Native-Ad-385x189.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/40-Casper_s-Native-Ad.png 1999w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>Puesto que ya había visitado su sitio, particularmente su página de producto, Casper me reorientó (retargeting) usando un ad de <a href="https://www.criteo.com/">Criteo</a>. De hecho, sabía que no era al azar porque el código de tracking era visible en la URL:</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="28" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/41-Casper-Retargeting-1024x28.png" alt="41 Casper Retargeting" class="wp-image-113902" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/41-Casper-Retargeting-1024x28.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/41-Casper-Retargeting-300x8.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/41-Casper-Retargeting-768x21.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/41-Casper-Retargeting-1536x42.png 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/41-Casper-Retargeting-380x10.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/41-Casper-Retargeting-600x17.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/41-Casper-Retargeting-760x21.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/41-Casper-Retargeting-1440x40.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/41-Casper-Retargeting-180x5.png 180w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/41-Casper-Retargeting-250x7.png 250w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/41-Casper-Retargeting-740x20.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/41-Casper-Retargeting-220x6.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/41-Casper-Retargeting-385x11.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/41-Casper-Retargeting.png 1999w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>Impactante. Realmente, impactante.</p>



<div class="wp-block-group is-style-shadow-box has-sleek-light-grey-background-color has-background"><div class="wp-block-group__inner-container">
<p><strong>Elemento de acción:&nbsp;</strong>Busca un sitio que (a) alabe tu marca y (b) permita ads o enlaces patrocinados en su sitio. Después, experimenta dirigiendo tráfico de Facebook a ese sitio y registra el número de derivaciones a través de los ads de ese sitio.</p>
</div></div>



<h2><strong>Parte 5: Marketing de email</strong></h2>



<p>Como muchos comercios online, Casper envía una variedad de emails de marketing.&nbsp;</p>



<p>Aquí me enfocaré en tres estrategias de email específicas que están usando para mover a los clientes potenciales a través de su embudo.</p>



<p>Continuemos.</p>



<h2 id="12"><strong>Estrategia #12: Usa este proceso de abandono de carrito de 3 pasos para recuperar ventas perdidas&nbsp;</strong></h2>



<p>Casper aprovecha un proceso de abandono de carrito de 2 pasos para recuperar a compradores indecisos.&nbsp;</p>



<p>Cuando abandoné mi carrito, recibí el primero de dos emails de recuperación de carrito un día después.&nbsp;</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="461" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/42-Casper_s-Cart-Recovery-Email-1024x461.png" alt="42 Casper_s Cart Recovery Email" class="wp-image-113906" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/42-Casper_s-Cart-Recovery-Email-1024x461.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/42-Casper_s-Cart-Recovery-Email-300x135.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/42-Casper_s-Cart-Recovery-Email-768x346.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/42-Casper_s-Cart-Recovery-Email-380x171.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/42-Casper_s-Cart-Recovery-Email-600x270.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/42-Casper_s-Cart-Recovery-Email-760x342.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/42-Casper_s-Cart-Recovery-Email-78x35.png 78w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/42-Casper_s-Cart-Recovery-Email-111x50.png 111w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/42-Casper_s-Cart-Recovery-Email-740x333.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/42-Casper_s-Cart-Recovery-Email-220x99.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/42-Casper_s-Cart-Recovery-Email-385x173.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/42-Casper_s-Cart-Recovery-Email.png 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>En este, Casper me invitó a completar mi compra. Nada nuevo. Pero debajo del llamado a la acción, estaba un GIF que resaltaba preguntas frecuentes, y una invitación para contactarlos si tenía alguna pregunta.</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="576" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/43-Casper_s-Cart-Recovery-Email-2-1024x576.gif" alt="43 Casper_s Cart Recovery Email 2" class="wp-image-113910" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/43-Casper_s-Cart-Recovery-Email-2-1024x576.gif 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/43-Casper_s-Cart-Recovery-Email-2-300x169.gif 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/43-Casper_s-Cart-Recovery-Email-2-768x432.gif 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/43-Casper_s-Cart-Recovery-Email-2-1536x864.gif 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/43-Casper_s-Cart-Recovery-Email-2-380x214.gif 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/43-Casper_s-Cart-Recovery-Email-2-600x338.gif 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/43-Casper_s-Cart-Recovery-Email-2-760x428.gif 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/43-Casper_s-Cart-Recovery-Email-2-1440x810.gif 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/43-Casper_s-Cart-Recovery-Email-2-62x35.gif 62w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/43-Casper_s-Cart-Recovery-Email-2-89x50.gif 89w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/43-Casper_s-Cart-Recovery-Email-2-740x416.gif 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/43-Casper_s-Cart-Recovery-Email-2-220x124.gif 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/43-Casper_s-Cart-Recovery-Email-2-385x217.gif 385w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>Invitar a visitantes que abandonan a ponerse en contacto no es solo un ejemplo de un buen servicio al cliente, sino que también es una forma excelente de superar potenciales objeciones que no fueron abordadas en la primera visita del cliente potencial. Además, Casper ofrece varias formas de ponerse en contacto, facilitando tanto como sea posible que tus preguntas sean respondidas y completes tu pedido.</p>



<p>Elegí no regresar a mi carrito. Así que, un día después, recibí un segundo email.&nbsp;</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="788" height="1024" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/44-Casper-Recovery-Email-2-788x1024.png" alt="44 Casper Recovery Email 2" class="wp-image-113914" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/44-Casper-Recovery-Email-2-788x1024.png 788w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/44-Casper-Recovery-Email-2-231x300.png 231w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/44-Casper-Recovery-Email-2-768x998.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/44-Casper-Recovery-Email-2-1182x1536.png 1182w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/44-Casper-Recovery-Email-2-380x494.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/44-Casper-Recovery-Email-2-600x780.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/44-Casper-Recovery-Email-2-760x988.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/44-Casper-Recovery-Email-2-27x35.png 27w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/44-Casper-Recovery-Email-2-38x50.png 38w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/44-Casper-Recovery-Email-2-377x490.png 377w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/44-Casper-Recovery-Email-2-220x286.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/44-Casper-Recovery-Email-2-385x501.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/44-Casper-Recovery-Email-2.png 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 788px) 100vw, 788px" /></figure></div>



<p>En este, Casper enfatiza la insuperable garantía que vimos en la Estrategia #1, haciéndome tan fácil como se puede que complete mi compra.</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="299" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/45-Casper-Guarantee-1024x299.png" alt="45 Casper Guarantee" class="wp-image-113918" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/45-Casper-Guarantee-1024x299.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/45-Casper-Guarantee-300x88.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/45-Casper-Guarantee-768x224.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/45-Casper-Guarantee-380x111.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/45-Casper-Guarantee-600x175.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/45-Casper-Guarantee-760x222.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/45-Casper-Guarantee-120x35.png 120w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/45-Casper-Guarantee-171x50.png 171w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/45-Casper-Guarantee-740x216.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/45-Casper-Guarantee-220x64.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/45-Casper-Guarantee-385x112.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/45-Casper-Guarantee.png 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>Lo más interesante sobre Casper es su capacidad de reconocer sus ventajas injustas (como su prueba gratuita de 100 noches) y usarlas en casa etapa de su marketing. Y en esto encontramos una moraleja importante:</p>



<p>Quizás no puedas competir con tu competidor cuando se trata de envíos gratis, garantías de 3 meses u otras expectativas que tienen los clientes. Pero puedes tomar lo que hace que tu negocio sea único y recordárselos a los clientes potenciales una y otra vez.&nbsp;</p>



<div class="wp-block-group is-style-shadow-box has-sleek-light-grey-background-color has-background"><div class="wp-block-group__inner-container">
<p><strong>Elemento de acción</strong>: Si tienes una tienda online y envías emails de recuperación de carrito, dales a los compradores potenciales una oportunidad para contactarte. Entonces, ayúdalos a superar sus objeciones para que puedan avanzar con su compra.</p>
</div></div>



<h2 id="13"><strong>Estrategia #13: Convierte a los clientes en vendedores con este motor de referencia replicable</strong></h2>



<p>Si leíste mi post sobre el <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/harrys-marketing" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">marketing de Harry’s</a>, sabes que Harry’s consiguió 100,000 direcciones de email en siete días… antes de que hicieran una venta.</p>



<p>Casper ha desarrollado un motor de derivaciones similar en su marketing y poscompra, invitando a los clientes a referir a sus amistades.</p>



<p>Así es como funciona.</p>



<p>Después de comprar en Casper, recibes un email de confirmación. Nada nuevo en esto. Pero después la cosa se torna interesante…</p>



<p>En el pie de página del email, hay un link de referido para derivar amistades y ganar recompensas.</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="538" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/46-Casper_s-Referral-Program-in-Email-Footer-1024x538.png" alt="46 Casper_s Referral Program in Email Footer" class="wp-image-113922" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/46-Casper_s-Referral-Program-in-Email-Footer-1024x538.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/46-Casper_s-Referral-Program-in-Email-Footer-300x158.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/46-Casper_s-Referral-Program-in-Email-Footer-768x403.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/46-Casper_s-Referral-Program-in-Email-Footer-380x200.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/46-Casper_s-Referral-Program-in-Email-Footer-600x315.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/46-Casper_s-Referral-Program-in-Email-Footer-760x399.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/46-Casper_s-Referral-Program-in-Email-Footer-67x35.png 67w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/46-Casper_s-Referral-Program-in-Email-Footer-95x50.png 95w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/46-Casper_s-Referral-Program-in-Email-Footer-740x389.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/46-Casper_s-Referral-Program-in-Email-Footer-220x116.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/46-Casper_s-Referral-Program-in-Email-Footer-385x202.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/46-Casper_s-Referral-Program-in-Email-Footer.png 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /><figcaption>Fuente: <a href="https://reallygoodemails.com/wp-content/uploads/thank-you-for-your-order-r650000650.html" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener nofollow">Really Good Emails</a></figcaption></figure></div>



<p>Esto crea una <em>brecha de curiosidad</em>. Las recompensas no están explicadas, así que te incita a hacer clic y saber más.</p>



<p>Cuando haces clic en “Conocer más”, te redirigen a una página en el sitio de Casper donde te ofrecen una tarjeta de regalo de Amazon a cambio de cada derivación que hagas.&nbsp;</p>



<p>¿La mejor parte?</p>



<p>Hacen que compartir el enlace sea simple, dependiendo de tu red social preferida.</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="497" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/47-Casper-Referral-Code-1024x497.png" alt="47 Casper Referral Code" class="wp-image-113926" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/47-Casper-Referral-Code-1024x497.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/47-Casper-Referral-Code-300x146.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/47-Casper-Referral-Code-768x373.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/47-Casper-Referral-Code-1536x746.png 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/47-Casper-Referral-Code-380x185.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/47-Casper-Referral-Code-600x291.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/47-Casper-Referral-Code-760x369.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/47-Casper-Referral-Code-1440x699.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/47-Casper-Referral-Code-72x35.png 72w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/47-Casper-Referral-Code-103x50.png 103w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/47-Casper-Referral-Code-740x359.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/47-Casper-Referral-Code-220x107.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/47-Casper-Referral-Code-385x187.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/47-Casper-Referral-Code.png 1999w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>Por ejemplo, si haces clic en “Email”, Casper activa un email ya redactado para que ni siquiera tengas que escribir el mensaje por tu cuenta.</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="710" height="610" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/48-Casper_s-Prewritten-Email.png" alt="48 Casper_s Prewritten Email" class="wp-image-113930" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/48-Casper_s-Prewritten-Email.png 710w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/48-Casper_s-Prewritten-Email-300x258.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/48-Casper_s-Prewritten-Email-380x326.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/48-Casper_s-Prewritten-Email-600x515.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/48-Casper_s-Prewritten-Email-41x35.png 41w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/48-Casper_s-Prewritten-Email-58x50.png 58w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/48-Casper_s-Prewritten-Email-570x490.png 570w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/48-Casper_s-Prewritten-Email-220x189.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/48-Casper_s-Prewritten-Email-385x331.png 385w" sizes="(max-width: 710px) 100vw, 710px" /></figure></div>



<p>Te ahorra tiempo, y es una buena forma de simplificar el dejar una reseña.</p>



<div class="wp-block-group is-style-shadow-box has-sleek-light-grey-background-color has-background"><div class="wp-block-group__inner-container">
<p><strong>Elemento de acción</strong>: Tus clientes son tus mejores vendedores. Así que invítalos a derivar a otros, e incentívalos por hacerlo. Quizás no puedas ofrecer tarjetas de regalo de Amazon (pocos pueden), pero puedes ofrecerles <em>algo</em> (ej., un descuento en su próxima compra).</p>
</div></div>



<h2 id="14"><strong>Estrategia #14: Obtén mejores reseñas de clientes con este simple, pero poderoso, truco de redacción</strong></h2>



<p>Como se mencionó antes, Casper usa sus emails de confirmación de pedido para invitar a sus nuevos clientes a referirlos a sus amigos.</p>



<p>Pero esa no ha sido siempre su estrategia…</p>



<p>Al principio, mientras desarrollaban su autoridad en su mercado, Casper construyó su reputación pidiendo <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/customer-testimonials" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">reseñas</a>.</p>



<p>Así era como funcionaba:</p>



<p>Unos días después de convertirte en un cliente nuevo, Casper te invitaba a dejar una reseña en su sitio.</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="858" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/49-Casper_s-Review-Email-1024x858.png" alt="49 Casper_s Review Email" class="wp-image-113934" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/49-Casper_s-Review-Email-1024x858.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/49-Casper_s-Review-Email-300x251.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/49-Casper_s-Review-Email-768x643.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/49-Casper_s-Review-Email-380x318.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/49-Casper_s-Review-Email-600x503.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/49-Casper_s-Review-Email-760x637.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/49-Casper_s-Review-Email-42x35.png 42w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/49-Casper_s-Review-Email-60x50.png 60w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/49-Casper_s-Review-Email-585x490.png 585w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/49-Casper_s-Review-Email-220x184.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/49-Casper_s-Review-Email-385x322.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/49-Casper_s-Review-Email.png 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>Después de hacer clic en el llamado a la acción, te redirigían a la página de reseñas de Casper. Allí, Casper te invitaba a dejar tu feedback usando varias preguntas como indicadores.</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="749" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/50-Casper_s-Review-Submission-Form-1024x749.png" alt="50 Casper_s Review Submission Form" class="wp-image-113938" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/50-Casper_s-Review-Submission-Form-1024x749.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/50-Casper_s-Review-Submission-Form-300x219.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/50-Casper_s-Review-Submission-Form-768x562.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/50-Casper_s-Review-Submission-Form-1536x1123.png 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/50-Casper_s-Review-Submission-Form-380x278.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/50-Casper_s-Review-Submission-Form-600x439.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/50-Casper_s-Review-Submission-Form-760x556.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/50-Casper_s-Review-Submission-Form-1440x1053.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/50-Casper_s-Review-Submission-Form-48x35.png 48w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/50-Casper_s-Review-Submission-Form-68x50.png 68w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/50-Casper_s-Review-Submission-Form-670x490.png 670w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/50-Casper_s-Review-Submission-Form-220x161.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/50-Casper_s-Review-Submission-Form-385x282.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/50-Casper_s-Review-Submission-Form.png 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>Casper sabe que cuando se les pide reseñas a los clientes, estos tienden a escribir reseñas genéricas. Por eso, en ese entonces, guiaban a los clientes para que escribieran sobre áreas importantes para ellos (Casper). Esto incluía la experiencia de desempacar (unboxing) y si el cliente recomendaría o no Casper a sus amigos.</p>



<p>Y funcionó.</p>



<p>Casper tiene cientos de reseñas que cumplen con todo lo anterior.</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="247" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/51-Casper-Review-1024x247.png" alt="51 Casper Review" class="wp-image-113942" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/51-Casper-Review-1024x247.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/51-Casper-Review-300x72.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/51-Casper-Review-768x185.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/51-Casper-Review-1536x370.png 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/51-Casper-Review-380x92.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/51-Casper-Review-600x145.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/51-Casper-Review-760x183.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/51-Casper-Review-1440x347.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/51-Casper-Review-145x35.png 145w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/51-Casper-Review-207x50.png 207w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/51-Casper-Review-740x178.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/51-Casper-Review-220x53.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/51-Casper-Review-385x93.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/51-Casper-Review.png 1680w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>Hoy en día, Casper reutiliza esas reseñas en su marketing, particularmente en sus emails de presentación. Este es el cuarto email que recibes después de registrarte de recibir novedades de Casper:</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="598" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/52-Review-in-Email-1024x598.png" alt="52 Review in Email" class="wp-image-113946" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/52-Review-in-Email-1024x598.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/52-Review-in-Email-300x175.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/52-Review-in-Email-768x449.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/52-Review-in-Email-380x222.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/52-Review-in-Email-600x351.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/52-Review-in-Email-760x444.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/52-Review-in-Email-60x35.png 60w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/52-Review-in-Email-86x50.png 86w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/52-Review-in-Email-740x432.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/52-Review-in-Email-220x129.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/52-Review-in-Email-385x225.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/52-Review-in-Email.png 1198w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>Ningún texto que escribas será mejor que la alabanza de un cliente. Así que usa las reseñas buenas en tus emails. Y úsalas a menudo.</p>



<div class="wp-block-group is-style-shadow-box has-sleek-light-grey-background-color has-background"><div class="wp-block-group__inner-container">
<p><strong>Elemento de acción</strong>: Invita a los nuevos clientes a reseñar su compra después de que pase suficiente tiempo. Entonces, guíalos sobre lo que pueden decir, basándote en potenciales objeciones a la compra de tus productos o áreas que quieras resaltar. Finalmente, reutiliza esas reseñas en todo tu marketing.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>
</div></div>


<div id="contentupgrade-block_5fc4ef58b50e4" class="block-content-upgrade">
    <div class="text">
        <p class="text-pretitle">RECURSOS GRATUITOS</p>
        <h2 class="text-title">Descarga el kit de herramientas de marketing de Casper </h2>
        <div class="text-content"><p>Me tomó 20 horas escribir este artículo. Veinte. Y está de más decir que hubo MUCHO que no pude incluir en el post. Para facilitarte la vida, he compilado un archivo swipe con los materiales de marketing de Casper. Además, un par de regalitos adicionales (*¡ejem!* una estrategia de bono que es muy buena como para ignorarla).</p>
<p>Accede al kit de herramientas de marketing de Casper y obtén más tráfico y un engagement más alto hoy (incluye contenido de bono que no está incluido en el post, ejemplos de email, ads de Facebook, y más).</p>
