										<content:encoded><![CDATA[
<h1 class="has-text-align-center"><strong>7 ejemplos de reseñas de clientes fáciles y eficaces que puedes copiar</strong></h1>
<div class="post-content-category"><a href="https://sleeknote.com/es/blog/category/conversion-rate-optimization" rel="category tag">Conversion Rate Optimization</a></div>


<figure class="wp-block-image alignwide size-large"><img width="1024" height="437" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Customer-Testimonials-Wordpress-1024x437.jpg" alt="Customer Testimonials [Wordpress]" class="wp-image-90454" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Customer-Testimonials-Wordpress-1024x437.jpg 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Customer-Testimonials-Wordpress-300x128.jpg 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Customer-Testimonials-Wordpress-768x328.jpg 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Customer-Testimonials-Wordpress-1536x656.jpg 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Customer-Testimonials-Wordpress-380x162.jpg 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Customer-Testimonials-Wordpress-600x256.jpg 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Customer-Testimonials-Wordpress-760x325.jpg 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Customer-Testimonials-Wordpress-1440x615.jpg 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Customer-Testimonials-Wordpress-960x410.jpg 960w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Customer-Testimonials-Wordpress-82x35.jpg 82w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Customer-Testimonials-Wordpress-117x50.jpg 117w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Customer-Testimonials-Wordpress-740x316.jpg 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Customer-Testimonials-Wordpress-220x94.jpg 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Customer-Testimonials-Wordpress-385x164.jpg 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Customer-Testimonials-Wordpress.jpg 1920w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure>


<div id="preamble-block_5e96c5c3c1348" class="block-preamble"><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">A mí me ha pasado. Y si estás leyendo esto, es que probablemente te haya pasado a ti también…</span></p>
</div>






<p>Lo das todo por un cliente y, a cambio, le pides que deje una reseña.</p>



<p>¿Y qué pasa cuando lo haces?</p>



<p><em>Cri cri</em>.&nbsp;</p>



<p>No hay respuesta. Ni rastro de reseña. Y te quedas sin ninguna&nbsp;<a rel="noreferrer noopener" href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/social-proof" target="_blank">prueba social</a> para tu marca.&nbsp;</p>



<p>Pero eso se acabó.&nbsp;</p>



<p>Hoy, vamos a ver siete tipos de reseñas de clientes que necesitas en tu estrategia de marketing para conseguir más conversiones, aumentar tus beneficios e infundir confianza en la marca.</p>


<div id="contentupgrade-block_5e96c5fdc1349" class="block-content-upgrade">
    <div class="text">
        <p class="text-pretitle">RECURSOS GRATUITOS</p>
        <h2 class="text-title">¿Quieres más ejemplos de reseñas de clientes?</h2>
        <div class="text-content"><p>Accede a nuestra biblioteca repleta de recursos de marketing gratuitos (con ejemplos de anuncios de Facebook, swipe file para lograr un mayor desempeño en las campañas de email, guías de marketing y más).</p>
</div>
                    <a onClick="SleekNote.triggerOnclick('00c91b9b-1dbc-48da-8d77-1dd2cfc8355b');" href="javascript:void(0);" class="text-link" title="Descarga tu guía práctica CRO ahora →">Descarga tu guía práctica CRO ahora →</a>
            </div>
    <div class="image">
        <img src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/Grow-Your-Email-List@2x-1.png" title="¿Quieres más ejemplos de reseñas de clientes?">    </div>
</div>


<h2><strong>Usa estos 7 ejemplos de reseñas para conseguir más clientes</strong></h2>



<p><a href="#1">Citas como reseñas</a></p>



<p><a href="#2">Reseñas de <em>influencers</em></a></p>



<p><a href="#3">Reseñas en redes sociales</a></p>



<p><a href="#4">Reseñas de clientes</a></p>



<p><a href="#5">Casos prácticos</a></p>



<p><a href="#6">Reseñas en vídeos</a></p>



<p><a href="#7">Series documentales</a></p>



<h2 id="1"><strong>1. Citas como reseñas</strong></h2>



<p>Hay tres tipos de citas como reseñas.&nbsp;</p>



<ol><li>Cita;</li><li>Cita con imagen destacada; y</li><li>Cita con imagen destacada y llamada a la acción (CTA)</li></ol>



<p>Veamos rápidamente cada una de ellas.&nbsp;</p>



<h3><strong>i. Citas</strong></h3>



<p>Todos estamos familiarizados con ellas. Y si tuviste la suerte de tener un anuario escolar, seguramente te pidieron una frase o cita para acompañar tu foto:</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="510" height="386" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Home-Simpson-Yearbook-Picture.png" alt="Home Simpson Yearbook Picture" class="wp-image-90466" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Home-Simpson-Yearbook-Picture.png 510w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Home-Simpson-Yearbook-Picture-300x227.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Home-Simpson-Yearbook-Picture-380x288.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Home-Simpson-Yearbook-Picture-46x35.png 46w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Home-Simpson-Yearbook-Picture-66x50.png 66w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Home-Simpson-Yearbook-Picture-220x167.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Home-Simpson-Yearbook-Picture-385x291.png 385w" sizes="(max-width: 510px) 100vw, 510px" /></figure></div>



<p>Las citas fueron uno de los primeros tipos de reseñas (y uno de los más sencillos). Comenzaron a aparecer en los periódicos y ahora son algo común en muchas páginas de productos. Tienen el fin de infundir confianza a posibles clientes y hacerles creer que están tomando una buena decisión.</p>



<p><a href="https://www.poopourri.com/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener nofollow">Poo~Pourri</a> utiliza un desplazador en su página principal para mostrar las opiniones de sus clientes:</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="505" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/PooPourri-Customer-Testimonial-1024x505.png" alt="Poo~Pourri Customer Testimonial" class="wp-image-90506" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/PooPourri-Customer-Testimonial-1024x505.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/PooPourri-Customer-Testimonial-300x148.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/PooPourri-Customer-Testimonial-768x378.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/PooPourri-Customer-Testimonial-1536x757.png 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/PooPourri-Customer-Testimonial-380x187.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/PooPourri-Customer-Testimonial-600x296.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/PooPourri-Customer-Testimonial-760x374.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/PooPourri-Customer-Testimonial-1440x710.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/PooPourri-Customer-Testimonial-71x35.png 71w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/PooPourri-Customer-Testimonial-101x50.png 101w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/PooPourri-Customer-Testimonial-740x365.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/PooPourri-Customer-Testimonial-220x108.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/PooPourri-Customer-Testimonial-385x190.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/PooPourri-Customer-Testimonial.png 1920w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>Añadir características adicionales como un desplazador (o en el caso de Poo~Pourri, un desplazador con clasificación de “estrellas”) hace que el lector participe y añade más validez a los testimonios.</p>



<h3><strong>ii. Citas con imagen destacada</strong></h3>



<p>Las citas, además de ser fáciles de conseguir, también son fáciles de hacer. Las empresas lo saben. Y por eso mismo muchas añaden imágenes a sus reseñas.</p>



<p>Las fotos hace que las reseñas sean más fiables y, en muchos casos, multiplican las conversiones.</p>



<p>De hecho, cuando <a href="http://www.160drivingacademy.com/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener nofollow">161 Driving Academy</a> reemplazó sus imágenes de portada por fotografías de personas reales, <a href="https://vwo.com/blog/stock-image-or-real-image/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener nofollow">sus índices de conversión aumentaron en un 161%</a>.</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="566" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/161-Driving-Academy-Split-Test-1024x566.png" alt="161 Driving Academy Split Test" class="wp-image-90410" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/161-Driving-Academy-Split-Test-1024x566.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/161-Driving-Academy-Split-Test-300x166.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/161-Driving-Academy-Split-Test-768x425.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/161-Driving-Academy-Split-Test-380x210.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/161-Driving-Academy-Split-Test-600x332.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/161-Driving-Academy-Split-Test-760x420.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/161-Driving-Academy-Split-Test-63x35.png 63w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/161-Driving-Academy-Split-Test-90x50.png 90w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/161-Driving-Academy-Split-Test-740x409.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/161-Driving-Academy-Split-Test-220x122.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/161-Driving-Academy-Split-Test-385x213.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/161-Driving-Academy-Split-Test.png 1242w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p><a href="https://www.shopify.com/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener nofollow">Shopify</a> incluye imágenes de portada de gran resolución para acompañar a sus reseñas. Cuando ves que una frase viene de un cliente como tú, es más fácil empatizar y continuar con la compra:</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="387" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Shopify-Customer-Testimonial-1024x387.png" alt="Shopify Customer Testimonial" class="wp-image-90514" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Shopify-Customer-Testimonial-1024x387.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Shopify-Customer-Testimonial-300x113.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Shopify-Customer-Testimonial-768x290.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Shopify-Customer-Testimonial-1536x580.png 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Shopify-Customer-Testimonial-380x143.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Shopify-Customer-Testimonial-600x227.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Shopify-Customer-Testimonial-760x287.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Shopify-Customer-Testimonial-1440x544.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Shopify-Customer-Testimonial-93x35.png 93w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Shopify-Customer-Testimonial-132x50.png 132w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Shopify-Customer-Testimonial-740x279.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Shopify-Customer-Testimonial-220x83.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Shopify-Customer-Testimonial-385x145.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Shopify-Customer-Testimonial.png 1920w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>Si a los clientes les apetece hablar de ti, ¿por qué no se lo muestras de manera positiva?<br></p>



<h3>iii. Citas con imagen destacada y llamada a la acción (CTA)<br></h3>



<p>¿Pensabas que una cita y una imagen destacada sería suficiente? Pues no.</p>



<p>Como vendedores, nunca podemos pensar que los posibles compradores saben qué hacer: tenemos que cogerles de la mano y mostrárselo. Y por eso los testimonios siempre necesitan una <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/call-to-action" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">llamada a la acción</a> (CTA) firme.</p>



<p>Siguiendo el ejemplo de Shopify, <a href="https://maruccisports.com/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener nofollow">Marucci</a> muestra una cita con una imágen destacada y un CTA, invitando a los lectores a leer un caso práctico:</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="475" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Marucci-Customer-Testimonials-1024x475.png" alt="Marucci Customer Testimonials" class="wp-image-90478" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Marucci-Customer-Testimonials-1024x475.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Marucci-Customer-Testimonials-300x139.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Marucci-Customer-Testimonials-768x356.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Marucci-Customer-Testimonials-1536x712.png 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Marucci-Customer-Testimonials-380x176.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Marucci-Customer-Testimonials-600x278.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Marucci-Customer-Testimonials-760x352.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Marucci-Customer-Testimonials-1440x668.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Marucci-Customer-Testimonials-76x35.png 76w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Marucci-Customer-Testimonials-108x50.png 108w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Marucci-Customer-Testimonials-740x343.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Marucci-Customer-Testimonials-220x102.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Marucci-Customer-Testimonials-385x178.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Marucci-Customer-Testimonials.png 1920w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>Si el visitante está interesado, puede aprender más sobre la transformación de David Ortiz antes de decidir si Marucci es para él o no.</p>



<p><a href="https://zapier.com/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener nofollow">Zapier</a> va un paso más allá con las opiniones de sus clientes. Y es un gran ejemplo de ese paso más. En vez de mostrar sus reseñas en una página determinada, los incluye en entradas destacadas.</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="348" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Zapier-Slide-In-Testimonial-1024x348.png" alt="Zapier Slide-In Testimonial" class="wp-image-90534" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Zapier-Slide-In-Testimonial-1024x348.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Zapier-Slide-In-Testimonial-300x102.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Zapier-Slide-In-Testimonial-768x261.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Zapier-Slide-In-Testimonial-380x129.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Zapier-Slide-In-Testimonial-600x204.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Zapier-Slide-In-Testimonial-760x258.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Zapier-Slide-In-Testimonial-103x35.png 103w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Zapier-Slide-In-Testimonial-147x50.png 147w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Zapier-Slide-In-Testimonial-740x251.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Zapier-Slide-In-Testimonial-220x75.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Zapier-Slide-In-Testimonial-385x131.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Zapier-Slide-In-Testimonial.png 1034w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<div class="wp-block-group is-style-shadow-box has-sleek-grey-background-color has-background"><div class="wp-block-group__inner-container">
<h3><strong>Nota del editor</strong></h3>



<p>Aquí tienes una manera rápida y sencilla de mostrar las reseñas correctas en las páginas adecuadas utilizando Sleeknote:</p>



<script src="https://fast.wistia.com/embed/medias/nrunfq9k0r.jsonp" async=""></script><script src="https://fast.wistia.com/assets/external/E-v1.js" async=""></script><div class="wistia_responsive_padding" style="padding:56.25% 0 0 0;position:relative;"><div class="wistia_responsive_wrapper" style="height:100%;left:0;position:absolute;top:0;width:100%;"><div class="wistia_embed wistia_async_nrunfq9k0r videoFoam=true" style="height:100%;position:relative;width:100%"><div class="wistia_swatch" style="height:100%;left:0;opacity:0;overflow:hidden;position:absolute;top:0;transition:opacity 200ms;width:100%;"><img src="https://fast.wistia.com/embed/medias/nrunfq9k0r/swatch" style="filter:blur(5px);height:100%;object-fit:contain;width:100%;" alt="" aria-hidden="true" onload="this.parentNode.style.opacity=1;"></div></div></div></div>
</div></div>



<div style="height:40px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>



<p>Una manera de diferenciarte al escribir testimonios es utilizando lo que los Copybloggers llaman <a href="http://www.copyblogger.com/testimonials-part-1/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener nofollow"><em>reverse testimonial</em></a>.&nbsp;</p>



<p>Esto es cuando una reseña comienza con la objeción del comprador, antes de continuar con halagos y terminar eclipsando al escepticismo del principio.</p>



<p>Aquí tienes un ejemplo de <a href="http://bonytobeastly.com/transformations/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener nofollow">Bony to Beastly</a>:</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="729" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Bony-to-Beastly-Customer-Testimonial-1024x729.png" alt="Bony to Beastly Customer Testimonial" class="wp-image-90426" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Bony-to-Beastly-Customer-Testimonial-1024x729.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Bony-to-Beastly-Customer-Testimonial-300x214.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Bony-to-Beastly-Customer-Testimonial-768x547.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Bony-to-Beastly-Customer-Testimonial-380x270.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Bony-to-Beastly-Customer-Testimonial-600x427.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Bony-to-Beastly-Customer-Testimonial-760x541.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Bony-to-Beastly-Customer-Testimonial-49x35.png 49w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Bony-to-Beastly-Customer-Testimonial-70x50.png 70w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Bony-to-Beastly-Customer-Testimonial-688x490.png 688w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Bony-to-Beastly-Customer-Testimonial-220x157.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Bony-to-Beastly-Customer-Testimonial-385x274.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Bony-to-Beastly-Customer-Testimonial.png 1110w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>En este ejemplo, Dallas habla sobre una preocupación que suelen tener los clientes potenciales al comprar por internet (“¿Será una estafa?”) antes de pasar a la transformación al realizar la acción (o en otras palabras, realizar una compra).</p>



<p class="has-sleek-light-grey-background-color has-background"><strong>Punto a seguir:</strong>&nbsp;Si utilizas citas como reseñas, asegúrate de que cada uno incluya su imagen destacada y un CTA relacionado que ofrezca a los visitantes la oportunidad de aprender más sobre la transformación del cliente, y no del producto.</p>



<h2 id="2"><strong>2. Reseñas de </strong><strong><em>influencers</em></strong></h2>



<p>Los <em>influencers </em>son como los chicos populares del instituto. Suelen ser conocidos entre las personas de la misma edad pero casi imposible de conseguir ser amigos.</p>



<p>Conseguir que el <em>influencer </em>te choque los cinco por el pasillo es admirable en sí. Pero lo que sí que es admirable (y donde deberías centrar tus actividades de divulgación) es conseguir salir en los medios, gracias a influencers, en <em>tu </em>mercado.</p>



<p>Piénsalo: Todo el mundo quiere salir en Entrepreneur, Forbes, The Huffington Post, etc. Pero hay un problema.</p>



<p><em>Todos van a por eso. </em>Es mejor hacerse notar por la gente importante que tu audiencia conozca.</p>



<p>Veamos <a href="http://www.dibruno.com/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener nofollow">Di Bruno Bros.</a> por ejemplo. Su especialidad son cestas de regalo gourmet y viajan por el mundo en busca de los mejores quesos, carnes y alimentos gourmet. Y sus esfuerzos valen la pena.</p>



<p>Habiendo llamado la atención de gigantes de la industria como <em>Travel + Leisure</em> y <em>Serious Eats </em>(entre otros), Di Bruno Bros combina citas con distintivos de marcas influyentes en su página:&nbsp;</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="491" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Di-Bruno-Bros.-Media-Testimonials-1024x491.png" alt="Di Bruno Bros. Media Testimonials" class="wp-image-90458" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Di-Bruno-Bros.-Media-Testimonials-1024x491.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Di-Bruno-Bros.-Media-Testimonials-300x144.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Di-Bruno-Bros.-Media-Testimonials-768x368.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Di-Bruno-Bros.-Media-Testimonials-1536x737.png 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Di-Bruno-Bros.-Media-Testimonials-380x182.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Di-Bruno-Bros.-Media-Testimonials-600x288.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Di-Bruno-Bros.-Media-Testimonials-760x365.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Di-Bruno-Bros.-Media-Testimonials-1440x691.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Di-Bruno-Bros.-Media-Testimonials-73x35.png 73w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Di-Bruno-Bros.-Media-Testimonials-104x50.png 104w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Di-Bruno-Bros.-Media-Testimonials-740x355.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Di-Bruno-Bros.-Media-Testimonials-220x106.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Di-Bruno-Bros.-Media-Testimonials-385x185.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Di-Bruno-Bros.-Media-Testimonials.png 1720w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>No siempre puedes atraer a <em>influencers</em>, eso está claro. Pero puedes aumentar las probabilidades de hacerte notar siendo el mejor en lo tuyo.</p>



<p class="has-sleek-light-grey-background-color has-background"><strong>Punto a seguir:</strong>&nbsp;Contacta con organismos importantes de tu sector y pregúntales si les gustaría probar tu producto.</p>



<h2 id="3"><strong>3. Reseñas en redes sociales</strong></h2>



<p>Las redes sociales han cambiado la manera en la que nos expresamos. Cuando no estamos poniendo en Instagram lo que estamos comiendo, damos voz a nuestros sueños, miedos y, a veces, frustraciones con nuestras marcas favoritas.</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="635" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Royal-Mail-Funny-Tweet-1024x635.png" alt="Royal Mail Funny Tweet" class="wp-image-90510" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Royal-Mail-Funny-Tweet-1024x635.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Royal-Mail-Funny-Tweet-300x186.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Royal-Mail-Funny-Tweet-768x477.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Royal-Mail-Funny-Tweet-380x236.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Royal-Mail-Funny-Tweet-600x372.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Royal-Mail-Funny-Tweet-760x472.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Royal-Mail-Funny-Tweet-56x35.png 56w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Royal-Mail-Funny-Tweet-81x50.png 81w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Royal-Mail-Funny-Tweet-740x459.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Royal-Mail-Funny-Tweet-220x137.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Royal-Mail-Funny-Tweet-385x239.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Royal-Mail-Funny-Tweet.png 1270w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>Cuando es positivo, todo el mundo acepta el elogio. Y con razón. Por encima de las citas, las reseñas sociales hacen efecto porque cabe la posibilidad de que entren en el enlace y vean que la persona sobre la que están leyendo es alguien <em>real</em>, con una vida <em>real</em>.&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>



<p><a rel="noreferrer noopener" href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/casper-marketing" target="_blank">Casper</a> incorpora tweets y entradas de Instagram de clientes en su página web para destacar la comodidad de sus productos: </p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="434" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Capser-Customer-Testimonial-1024x434.png" alt="Capser Customer Testimonial" class="wp-image-90430" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Capser-Customer-Testimonial-1024x434.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Capser-Customer-Testimonial-300x127.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Capser-Customer-Testimonial-768x326.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Capser-Customer-Testimonial-1536x651.png 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Capser-Customer-Testimonial-380x161.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Capser-Customer-Testimonial-600x254.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Capser-Customer-Testimonial-760x322.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Capser-Customer-Testimonial-1440x611.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Capser-Customer-Testimonial-83x35.png 83w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Capser-Customer-Testimonial-118x50.png 118w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Capser-Customer-Testimonial-740x314.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Capser-Customer-Testimonial-220x93.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Capser-Customer-Testimonial-385x163.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Capser-Customer-Testimonial.png 1580w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>Fabletics anima a sus clientes a compartir imágenes de ellos mismos utilizando su producto en Instagram con el hashtag #MyFabletics&#8230;</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="473" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/My-Fabletics-Instagram-Posts-1024x473.png" alt="My Fabletics Instagram Posts" class="wp-image-90490" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/My-Fabletics-Instagram-Posts-1024x473.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/My-Fabletics-Instagram-Posts-300x139.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/My-Fabletics-Instagram-Posts-768x355.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/My-Fabletics-Instagram-Posts-1536x710.png 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/My-Fabletics-Instagram-Posts-380x176.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/My-Fabletics-Instagram-Posts-600x277.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/My-Fabletics-Instagram-Posts-760x351.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/My-Fabletics-Instagram-Posts-1440x665.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/My-Fabletics-Instagram-Posts-76x35.png 76w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/My-Fabletics-Instagram-Posts-108x50.png 108w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/My-Fabletics-Instagram-Posts-740x342.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/My-Fabletics-Instagram-Posts-220x102.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/My-Fabletics-Instagram-Posts-385x178.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/My-Fabletics-Instagram-Posts.png 1905w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>&#8230;y lo hacen.</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="518" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/My-Fabletics-Top-Posts-1024x518.png" alt="My Fabletics Top Posts" class="wp-image-90494" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/My-Fabletics-Top-Posts-1024x518.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/My-Fabletics-Top-Posts-300x152.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/My-Fabletics-Top-Posts-768x388.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/My-Fabletics-Top-Posts-1536x777.png 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/My-Fabletics-Top-Posts-380x192.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/My-Fabletics-Top-Posts-600x303.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/My-Fabletics-Top-Posts-760x384.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/My-Fabletics-Top-Posts-1440x728.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/My-Fabletics-Top-Posts-69x35.png 69w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/My-Fabletics-Top-Posts-99x50.png 99w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/My-Fabletics-Top-Posts-740x374.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/My-Fabletics-Top-Posts-220x111.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/My-Fabletics-Top-Posts-385x195.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/My-Fabletics-Top-Posts.png 1720w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>El hashtag #MyFabletics se ha utilizado <em>más de 37,000 veces:</em></p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="382" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/My-Fabletics-Hashtag-1024x382.png" alt="My Fabletics Hashtag" class="wp-image-90486" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/My-Fabletics-Hashtag-1024x382.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/My-Fabletics-Hashtag-300x112.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/My-Fabletics-Hashtag-768x286.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/My-Fabletics-Hashtag-380x142.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/My-Fabletics-Hashtag-600x224.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/My-Fabletics-Hashtag-760x283.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/My-Fabletics-Hashtag-94x35.png 94w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/My-Fabletics-Hashtag-134x50.png 134w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/My-Fabletics-Hashtag-740x276.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/My-Fabletics-Hashtag-220x82.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/My-Fabletics-Hashtag-385x144.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/My-Fabletics-Hashtag.png 1100w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p class="has-sleek-light-grey-background-color has-background"><strong>Punto a seguir:</strong>&nbsp;Invita a los clientes a que dejen reseñas en redes sociales después de que hagan una compra. Después, incluye cualquier reseña positiva en la página de tus productos.</p>



<h2 id="4"><strong>4. Reseñas de clientes&nbsp;</strong></h2>



<p>Probablemente estés familiarizado con la prueba social. Si no es así, una prueba social <em>tiende a suponer que las acciones de otros reflejan el comportamiento correcto de una situación</em>.</p>



<p>Pero no todas las formas de influencia son iguales. Lo más importante es cuando las acciones de otros pertenecen a personas que son <em>parecidas </em>a nosotros.</p>



<p><a href="http://journals.plos.org/plosone/article/file?type=supplementary&amp;id=info:doi/10.1371/journal.pone.0106606.s001" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener nofollow">Un estudio de&nbsp;2008</a> reveló que era más probable que los clientes de hoteles reutilizaran sus toallas si se les decía que casi todos los clientes anteriores de la <em>misma habitación</em> lo hicieron así, que aquellos que se leyeron las normas generales del hotel.&nbsp;</p>



<p>Viéndolo de otra forma, <em>preferimos personas que piensen de manera parecida a nosotros.</em> Si te pareces a un comprador anterior, es más probable que estés receptivo a sus reseñas. No es ninguna sorpresa saber que somos <em>bastante </em>sensibles a las opiniones de otros clientes.</p>



<p>De hecho, <a href="https://www2.deloitte.com/content/dam/Deloitte/uk/Documents/consumer-business/consumer-review-8-the-growing-power-of-consumers.pdf" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener nofollow">según un estudio de Deloitte</a>, el 60% de las personas califica las reseñas como <em>igual de fiables</em> que la información que obtienen de amigos y familiares.</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="592" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Most-Trusted-Source-of-Information-on-Products-and-Services-1024x592.png" alt="Most Trusted Source of Information on Products and Services" class="wp-image-90482" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Most-Trusted-Source-of-Information-on-Products-and-Services-1024x592.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Most-Trusted-Source-of-Information-on-Products-and-Services-300x174.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Most-Trusted-Source-of-Information-on-Products-and-Services-768x444.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Most-Trusted-Source-of-Information-on-Products-and-Services-380x220.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Most-Trusted-Source-of-Information-on-Products-and-Services-600x347.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Most-Trusted-Source-of-Information-on-Products-and-Services-760x440.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Most-Trusted-Source-of-Information-on-Products-and-Services-61x35.png 61w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Most-Trusted-Source-of-Information-on-Products-and-Services-86x50.png 86w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Most-Trusted-Source-of-Information-on-Products-and-Services-740x428.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Most-Trusted-Source-of-Information-on-Products-and-Services-220x127.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Most-Trusted-Source-of-Information-on-Products-and-Services-385x223.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Most-Trusted-Source-of-Information-on-Products-and-Services.png 1340w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>Algunas marcas como <a rel="noreferrer noopener" href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/harrys-marketing" target="_blank">Harry’s</a>, una empresa de afeitado masculino, utiliza <a href="https://www.trustpilot.com/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener nofollow">TrustPilot</a> para mejorar su credibilidad.</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="453" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Harry_s-Trustpilot-Reviews-1024x453.png" alt="Harry_s Trustpilot Reviews" class="wp-image-90462" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Harry_s-Trustpilot-Reviews-1024x453.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Harry_s-Trustpilot-Reviews-300x133.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Harry_s-Trustpilot-Reviews-768x340.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Harry_s-Trustpilot-Reviews-1536x680.png 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Harry_s-Trustpilot-Reviews-380x168.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Harry_s-Trustpilot-Reviews-600x266.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Harry_s-Trustpilot-Reviews-760x336.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Harry_s-Trustpilot-Reviews-1440x638.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Harry_s-Trustpilot-Reviews-79x35.png 79w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Harry_s-Trustpilot-Reviews-113x50.png 113w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Harry_s-Trustpilot-Reviews-740x328.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Harry_s-Trustpilot-Reviews-220x97.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Harry_s-Trustpilot-Reviews-385x170.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Harry_s-Trustpilot-Reviews.png 1920w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>Las reseñas de clientes suele ser&nbsp; el tipo más fácil de reseñas porque son <em>super </em>fáciles de conseguir. De hecho, <a href="http://reallygoodemails.com/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener nofollow">Casper envía un correo después de una compra</a> pidiendo a sus clientes que dejen una opinión:</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="790" height="670" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper-Review-Email.png" alt="Casper Review Email" class="wp-image-90438" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper-Review-Email.png 790w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper-Review-Email-300x254.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper-Review-Email-768x651.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper-Review-Email-380x322.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper-Review-Email-600x509.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper-Review-Email-760x645.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper-Review-Email-41x35.png 41w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper-Review-Email-59x50.png 59w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper-Review-Email-578x490.png 578w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper-Review-Email-220x187.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Casper-Review-Email-385x327.png 385w" sizes="(max-width: 790px) 100vw, 790px" /></figure></div>



<p class="has-sleek-light-grey-background-color has-background"><strong>Punto a seguir:</strong>&nbsp;Envía un email a los clientes 14 días después de su compra para que dejen una reseña en un sitio web importante en el sector. Después, muestra estas reseñas en tu página web.</p>



<h2 id="5"><strong>5. Casos prácticos</strong></h2>



<p>Los casos prácticos son una oportunidad de vender <em>de verdad</em> al lector la transformación que hizo un cliente anterior.</p>



<p>Con la <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/e-commerce-copywriting" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">fórmula del copywriting</a> como Before-After-Bridge (BAB), puedes mostrar a los lectores dónde estaba un cliente <em>antes </em>de que hiciera su compra, dónde está ahora, <em>después </em>de realizar una compra, y tender un puente utilizando tu producto o servicio.</p>



<p><a href="https://blog.bufferapp.com/copywriting-formulas" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener nofollow">Kevan Lee de Buffer</a> resume la fórmula BAB muy bien:</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="356" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Before-After-Bridge-Formula-1024x356.png" alt="Before After Bridge Formula" class="wp-image-90418" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Before-After-Bridge-Formula-1024x356.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Before-After-Bridge-Formula-300x104.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Before-After-Bridge-Formula-768x267.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Before-After-Bridge-Formula-1536x534.png 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Before-After-Bridge-Formula-380x132.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Before-After-Bridge-Formula-600x209.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Before-After-Bridge-Formula-760x264.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Before-After-Bridge-Formula-1440x501.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Before-After-Bridge-Formula-101x35.png 101w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Before-After-Bridge-Formula-144x50.png 144w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Before-After-Bridge-Formula-740x257.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Before-After-Bridge-Formula-220x76.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Before-After-Bridge-Formula-385x134.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Before-After-Bridge-Formula.png 1755w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>Steve Kamb de <a href="https://www.nerdfitness.com/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener nofollow"><em>Nerd Fitness</em></a> utiliza casos prácticos para <a rel="noreferrer noopener" href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/list-building-strategies" target="_blank">generar clientes potenciales</a> para su producto estrella, The NerdFitness Academy. Kamb ofrece sabiamente <a rel="noreferrer noopener" href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/e-commerce-email-marketing" target="_blank">emails para clientes</a> para promover su historia, legitimando el caso práctico en el proceso:</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="814" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Nerd-Fitness-Customer-Testimonial-1024x814.png" alt="Nerd Fitness Customer Testimonial" class="wp-image-90498" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Nerd-Fitness-Customer-Testimonial-1024x814.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Nerd-Fitness-Customer-Testimonial-300x238.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Nerd-Fitness-Customer-Testimonial-768x611.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Nerd-Fitness-Customer-Testimonial-380x302.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Nerd-Fitness-Customer-Testimonial-600x477.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Nerd-Fitness-Customer-Testimonial-760x604.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Nerd-Fitness-Customer-Testimonial-44x35.png 44w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Nerd-Fitness-Customer-Testimonial-63x50.png 63w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Nerd-Fitness-Customer-Testimonial-616x490.png 616w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Nerd-Fitness-Customer-Testimonial-220x175.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Nerd-Fitness-Customer-Testimonial-385x306.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Nerd-Fitness-Customer-Testimonial.png 1190w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p class="has-sleek-light-grey-background-color has-background"><strong>Punto a seguir:</strong>&nbsp;Invita a un cliente anterior a que cuente su historia después de usar tu producto, y céntrate en la transformación que tuvieron.</p>



<h2 id="6"><strong>6. Reseñas en vídeos</strong></h2>



<p>El vídeo se está convirtiendo rápidamente en el canal de marketing número uno para los empresarios.&nbsp;</p>



<p>De hecho, <a href="https://www.emarketer.com/Article/Which-Content-Marketing-Tactics-Best-ROI/1009706" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener nofollow">según un informe de Copypress</a>, el 51.9% de profesionales del marketing de todo el mundo piensa que el vídeo es el tipo de contenido con el mejor ROI.</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="860" height="745" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Content-with-Best-ROI.png" alt="Content with Best ROI" class="wp-image-90442" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Content-with-Best-ROI.png 860w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Content-with-Best-ROI-300x260.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Content-with-Best-ROI-768x665.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Content-with-Best-ROI-380x329.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Content-with-Best-ROI-600x520.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Content-with-Best-ROI-760x658.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Content-with-Best-ROI-40x35.png 40w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Content-with-Best-ROI-58x50.png 58w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Content-with-Best-ROI-566x490.png 566w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Content-with-Best-ROI-220x191.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Content-with-Best-ROI-385x334.png 385w" sizes="(max-width: 860px) 100vw, 860px" /></figure></div>



<p>Marcas como Harry’s y Orabrush se hicieron virales aparentemente de la noche a la mañana aprovechándose del poder del vídeo para promover sus servicios. En palabras de <a href="https://www.quicksprout.com/2013/11/27/if-a-picture-says-1000-words-than-video-is-priceless/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener nofollow">Neil Patel</a>: <em>“Si una imagen vale más que mil palabras, entonces el vídeo tiene un valor incalculable”.</em></p>



<p>Pero el vídeo no se limita a la comercialización del producto. Ramit Sethi de <a href="http://www.iwillteachyoutoberich.com/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener nofollow"><em>I Will Teach You to Be Rich</em></a><em> </em>utiliza los vídeos para comercializar su producto estrella, Zero to Launch—pero con una peculiaridad. En vez de centrarse en el beneficio para el espectador, Ramit se hace diferenciar centrándose en la transformación de clientes <em>anteriores</em>.</p>



<p>Ramit da a conocer a sus estudiantes más exitosos para que vendan su curso por él, mediante la combinación del valor de producción profesional con entrevistas reveladoras y casos prácticos. (Observa la caja “Success Story Quick Wins” de encima del vídeo para echar un vistazo a los lectores):</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="505" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Maria-B.-Success-Story-1024x505.png" alt="Maria B. Success Story" class="wp-image-90474" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Maria-B.-Success-Story-1024x505.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Maria-B.-Success-Story-300x148.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Maria-B.-Success-Story-768x378.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Maria-B.-Success-Story-1536x757.png 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Maria-B.-Success-Story-380x187.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Maria-B.-Success-Story-600x296.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Maria-B.-Success-Story-760x374.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Maria-B.-Success-Story-1440x710.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Maria-B.-Success-Story-71x35.png 71w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Maria-B.-Success-Story-101x50.png 101w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Maria-B.-Success-Story-740x365.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Maria-B.-Success-Story-220x108.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Maria-B.-Success-Story-385x190.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Maria-B.-Success-Story.png 1920w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>Otros vendedores, como el ya mencionado Orabrush, muestran las reseñas de clientes en su página principal:</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="340" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Orabrush-Customer-Testimonials-1024x340.png" alt="Orabrush Customer Testimonials" class="wp-image-90502" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Orabrush-Customer-Testimonials-1024x340.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Orabrush-Customer-Testimonials-300x100.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Orabrush-Customer-Testimonials-768x255.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Orabrush-Customer-Testimonials-380x126.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Orabrush-Customer-Testimonials-600x199.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Orabrush-Customer-Testimonials-760x252.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Orabrush-Customer-Testimonials-106x35.png 106w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Orabrush-Customer-Testimonials-151x50.png 151w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Orabrush-Customer-Testimonials-740x245.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Orabrush-Customer-Testimonials-220x73.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Orabrush-Customer-Testimonials-385x128.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Orabrush-Customer-Testimonials.png 1034w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>Hace mucho tiempo, las reseñas en vídeo estaban reservadas para empresas con presupuestos de marketing de 6 cifras. Pero, hoy en día, cualquiera puede grabar un vídeo en cualquier parte, en cualquier momento y capturar lo que piensan sobre sus marcas favoritas.</p>



<p class="has-sleek-light-grey-background-color has-background"><strong>Punto a seguir:</strong>&nbsp;Pide a los clientes que graben un testimonio en vídeo con sus smartphones hablando sobre lo que más les ha gustado sobre tu marca. Después, muéstralo a clientes potenciales en los momentos más críticos del trayecto de un comprador.</p>



<h2 id="7"><strong>7. Series documentales</strong></h2>



<p>Como la mayoría de vendedores, pensaba que había visto todo sobre reseñas de clientes. Hasta que me encontré con Bryan Harris.</p>



<p>En 2016, Bryan lanzó su producto estrella, Get 10,000 Subscribers, pero fue más allá al entrevistar a clientes anteriores: <em>Grabó una serie documental.</em></p>



<p>Con cámara en mano, Bryan hizo una visita a tres antiguos estudiantes para documentar cómo habían cambiado sus vidas después de finalizar el curso.</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="580" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Underrated-1024x580.png" alt="Underrated" class="wp-image-90526" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Underrated-1024x580.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Underrated-300x170.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Underrated-768x435.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Underrated-380x215.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Underrated-600x340.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Underrated-760x431.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Underrated-62x35.png 62w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Underrated-88x50.png 88w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Underrated-740x419.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Underrated-220x125.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Underrated-385x218.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/Underrated.png 1034w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>Y los resultados fueron impresionantes.</p>



<p>A los espectadores les encantó, los clientes potenciales compraron el producto de Bryan como nunca antes y los <a href="http://videofruit.com/blog/2016-year-review/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener nofollow">ingresos pasaron de 900,000$ a 1.5 millones de dólares</a> en menos de 12 meses:</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="575" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/VideoFruit-Yearly-Booked-Revenue-1024x575.png" alt="VideoFruit Yearly Booked Revenue" class="wp-image-90530" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/VideoFruit-Yearly-Booked-Revenue-1024x575.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/VideoFruit-Yearly-Booked-Revenue-300x168.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/VideoFruit-Yearly-Booked-Revenue-768x431.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/VideoFruit-Yearly-Booked-Revenue-380x213.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/VideoFruit-Yearly-Booked-Revenue-600x337.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/VideoFruit-Yearly-Booked-Revenue-760x427.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/VideoFruit-Yearly-Booked-Revenue-62x35.png 62w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/VideoFruit-Yearly-Booked-Revenue-89x50.png 89w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/VideoFruit-Yearly-Booked-Revenue-740x416.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/VideoFruit-Yearly-Booked-Revenue-220x124.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/VideoFruit-Yearly-Booked-Revenue-385x216.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/04/VideoFruit-Yearly-Booked-Revenue.png 1095w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>Aunque es imposible saber el impacto que tuvo el documental directamente en los ingresos anuales de Videofruit (solo Bryan lo sabe), pocos pueden negar el poder de influencia de destacar el éxito de los clientes.&nbsp;</p>



<p>Hay algo sobre proporcionar a los posibles clientes una visión de lo que podrían ser sus vidas si hicieran una compra; una que lleva a la comercialización del producto a otro nivel.</p>



<p>Grabar un documental no es algo que pueda hacer todo el mundo. Y puede que no sea la mejor opción para ti o tu negocio. Pero cada vez más empresarios optan por vídeos profesionales para comercializar sus productos. Y con razón: funciona.</p>



<p class="has-sleek-light-grey-background-color has-background"><strong>Punto a seguir:</strong>&nbsp;Pregunta a tus clientes actuales en qué han cambiado sus vidas después de comprar tu producto y muéstralo en un documental destacando sus transformaciones.</p>



<div style="height:40px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"></div>


